ressive%20upward%20curve%20for%20the%20party%2C%20considering%20the%20fact%20that%20in%201984%20when%20it%20had%20contested%20the%20parliamentary%20elections%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20it%20could%20grab%20only%20two%20seats.%20This%20was%2C%20of%20course%2C%20much%20less%20than%20what%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20predecessor%2C%20the%20Jana%20Sangh%20had%20got%20before%20it%20became%20the%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%201991%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20not%20only%20reap%20a%20rich%20electoral%20harvest%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20which%20has%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20number%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20but%20the%20party%20also%20saw%20its%20vote%20share%20shoot%20up%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20including%20southern%20India.%20From%207.4%25%20in%201984%2C%20and%2011.4%25%20in%201989%2C%20it%20surged%20to%2020.1%25%20in%201991%2C%20which%20eventually%20cleared%20the%20path%20for%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20to%20become%20the%20single%20largest%20in%20the%20next%20general%20elections%20in%201996.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20in%201997%2C%20the%20party%20could%20return%20to%20power%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20it%20winning%20more%20seats%20in%20the%20assemblies%20of%20some%20other%20Hindi%20heartland%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20373px)%2085vw%2C%20373px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F15133951%2Fmodi-advani.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Narendra%20Modi%20with%20L.K.%20Advani%20during%20Advani's%20rath%20yatra.%20Credit%3A%20Twitter%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22373%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F15133951%2Fmodi-advani.jpg%20454w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F15133951%2Fmodi-advani-300x272.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-205233%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22338%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20with%20L.K.%20Advani%20during%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20rath%20yatra.%20Credit%3A%20Twitter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20single%20most%20important%20reason%20for%20that%20firm%20and%20steady%20rise%20is%20widely%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20L.K.%20Advani-led%20Rath%20Yatra%20to%20Ayodhya%20in%201990%20%E2%80%93%20where%20he%20rode%20a%20Toyota-rath%20on%20the%20strident%20demand%20to%20build%20a%20Ram%20temple%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20stood.%20It%20was%20a%20response%20to%20the%20Mandal%20report%20being%20accepted%20by%20the%20V.P.%20Singh%20government%20which%20threw%20a%20spanner%20in%20the%20works%20of%20the%20BJP%20which%20had%20until%20then%20been%20supporting%20the%20government.%20Kalyan%20Singh%20could%20successfully%20fashion%20a%20victory%20around%20that%20strong%20Hindu%20sentiment%20for%20a%20Ram%20Mandir%20at%20Ayodhya%20and%20formed%20a%20government%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20January%2022%2C%20when%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20virtually%20don%20the%20role%20of%20a%20priest%20at%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20no%20stone%20would%20be%20left%20unturned%20in%20trying%20to%20re-run%20the%20old%20theme%2C%20and%20use%20the%20ceremony%20to%20be%20able%20to%20win%20another%20general%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition%E2%80%99s%20false%20dilemma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ceremony%20is%20also%20being%20weaponised%20to%20checkmate%20the%20opposition%20which%20is%20threatening%20to%20contest%20the%202024%20elections%20unitedly%20against%20the%20BJP.%20Accordingly%2C%20invitations%20have%20been%20dispatched%20to%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20top%20leaders%20like%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20CPI%20(M)%20general%20secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20leader%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20while%20also%20steering%20clear%20of%20the%20likes%20of%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20%E2%80%93%20lest%20his%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20draw%20any%20traction%20electorally%20in%20Maharashtra%20from%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInvited%20formally%20or%20not%2C%20January%2022%20has%20put%20several%20opposition%20leaders%20in%20a%20bind%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20or%20not%20to%20join%20the%20ceremony%20led%20by%20the%20ruling%20party.%20Their%20dilemma%20essentially%20springs%20out%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Ram%20temple%20issue%20has%20an%20undeniable%20link%20to%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20millions%20of%20believing%20Hindus.%20Whether%20they%20show%20up%20at%20the%20January%2022%20ceremony%20or%20not%2C%20here%20are%20two%20arguments%20they%20must%20be%20able%20to%20present%20to%20the%20voters%20to%20be%20able%20to%20cut%20through%20the%20trap%20they%20find%20themselves%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERam%20is%20above%20politics%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20the%20January%2022%20ceremony%20will%20be%20led%20not%20by%20any%20Hindu%20religious%20leader%20but%20by%20Modi%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20only%20face%2C%20gives%20the%20game%20away.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patrika.com%2Fayodhya-news%2Fram-mandir-inauguration-puri-shankaracharya-not-go-ayodhya-comment-on-pm-modi-8665759%2F%5C%22%3EShankaracharya%20has%20already%20said%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20go%20to%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20needs%20a%20pan-India%20narrative%20to%20surmount%20a%2010-year%20incumbency%20load%20%E2%80%93%20one%20which%20is%20much%20more%20emotive%20than%20Kashmir%20or%20Pakistan%20bogeys%2C%20and%20this%20is%20particularly%20true%20for%20southern%20and%20eastern%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20significant%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20trusted%20aide%20and%20former%20principal%20secretary%20at%20the%20PMO%2C%20Nripendra%20Mishra%2C%20was%20placed%20at%20Ayodhya%20to%20head%20the%20temple%20construction%20committee%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janambhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra.%20That%20project%20under%20Mishra%20is%20set%20to%20plant%20Modi%20this%20January%2022%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20Hriday%20Samrat%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20then%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20must%20be%20able%20to%20hold%20up%20to%20their%20voters%20is%20a%20simple%20but%20assertive%20line%20that%20the%20deity%2C%20Ram%2C%20is%20above%20politics.%20They%20must%20say%20that%20people%E2%80%99s%20religious%20sentiments%20must%20not%20be%20permitted%20to%20become%20a%20tool%20for%20a%20political%20party%20which%20is%20desperate%20to%20win%20an%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20being%20an%20ardent%20Hindu%2C%20a%20believer%20of%20Ram%2C%20is%20different%20from%20being%20a%20BJP%20voter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20.jpg%20650w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20-300x185.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-629759%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20design%20for%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20vote%20for%20any%20party%20in%20an%20election%2C%20a%20conscious%20citizen%20must%20ask%20questions%20that%20affect%20the%20quality%20of%20her%20day-to-day%20life.%20So%2C%20before%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20too%2C%20voters%20must%20ask%20the%20Modi%20government%3A%20What%20has%20it%20done%20to%20create%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20to%20control%20price%20rise%2C%20to%20make%20healthcare%20and%20education%20accessible%2C%20and%20to%20ensure%20our%20borders%20are%20safe%20and%20secure%3F%20The%20Ram%20temple%20is%20being%20constructed%20due%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fayodhya-verdict-supreme-court-judgment%5C%22%3Efavourable%20judgment%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20opposition%20could%20do%20well%20to%20remind%20voters%20of%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20on%20January%2022%2C%20it%20would%20also%20be%20worthwhile%20for%20opposition%20leaders%20to%20remind%20all%20conscious%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%20about%20the%20father%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20Mahatma%20Gandhi.%20While%20falling%20to%20the%20bullets%20pumped%20into%20his%20frail%20body%20by%20a%20fanatic%20during%20a%20prayer%20meeting%2C%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20last%20words%20were%2C%20%E2%80%98Hey%20Ram%E2%80%99.%20That%20utterance%20should%20signify%20how%20much%20of%20an%20ardent%20Ram%20worshipper%20he%20was%2C%20perhaps%20different%20from%20the%20one%20who%20took%20his%20life%2C%20a%20former%20member%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20the%20ideological%20fount%20of%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20democracy%2C%20stupid%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20January%2022%2C%20opposition%20leaders%20must%20be%20able%20to%20convey%20to%20the%20voters%20that%20if%20they%20attend%20the%20ceremony%2C%20they%20would%20only%20be%20standing%20behind%20a%20BJP%20leader%20who%20would%20be%20using%20all%20possible%20media%20under%20his%20command%20(and%20there%20are%20very%20few%20honourable%20exceptions%20left)%20to%20launch%20a%20grand%20campaign%20for%20his%20party%20to%20be%20able%20to%20win%20a%20crucial%20election.%20The%20party%20and%20its%20main%20mascot%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-rss-bjp-vhp-ram-temple%5C%22%3Ebrazenly%20hoping%20to%20milk%20religious%20sentiments%20for%20votes.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbove%20all%2C%20non-BJP%20leaders%20should%20be%20able%20to%20remind%20all%20patriotic%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%20that%20it%20is%20the%20citizen%20who%20is%20the%20sovereign%2C%20and%20proud%20custodians%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy.%20That%20acknowledgment%20comes%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20democracy%20is%20run%20by%20a%20constitution%3B%20and%2C%20that%20no%20constitution%20in%20any%20democracy%2C%20including%20ours%2C%20mandates%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20be%20a%20monarch%20or%20a%20priest.%20We%20are%20not%20a%20constitutional%20monarchy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECountries%20often%20require%20moments%20of%20clarity%20like%20this%20one.%20This%20may%20well%20be%20one%20where%20the%20courage%20to%20call%20it%20what%20it%20is%20decides%20the%20shape%20of%20the%20years%20to%20come.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704796258000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F21170011%2F1_Ayodhya_Ram_Paidi_Uttar_Pradesh_India_2013.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-january-22-modi-opposition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22They%20will%20be%20rewarded%20for%20courage%20and%20ability%20to%20call%20out%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20aim%20of%20politicising%20religion.%20Lining%20up%20behind%20as%20Modi%20as%20he%20behaves%20as%20'yajman'%20won%E2%80%99t%20win%20them%20votes%2C%20but%20will%20be%20a%20mockery%20of%20the%20country%20as%20a%20whole.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-january-22-modi-opposition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Germany%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup-Winning%20Player%2C%20Coach%20Franz%20Beckenbauer%20Passes%20Away%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09152605%2FCmvy8BWXgAA0-TG.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFranz%20Anton%20Beckenbauer%20believed%20in%20reincarnation.%20%E2%80%9CMaybe%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20here%20once%20before%2C%20as%20a%20plant%20or%20something%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20a%20Berlin%20newspaper%20in%201994.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20not%20been%20able%20to%20transport%20myself%20back%20yet%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20something%20I%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20do.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20knows%20how%20many%20lives%20Beckenbauer%20had%20already%20lived%2C%20or%20as%20what%2C%20before%20the%20one%20which%20ended%20on%20January%207%2C%202024%2C%20after%20his%20family%20informed%20the%20German%20press%20agency%20dpa%20he%20passed%20away%20peacefully%20on%20Sunday%20surrounded%20by%20his%20family.%20He%20was%2078.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20he%20had%20been%20in%20a%20previous%20life%2C%20whatever%20he%20had%20done%2C%20it%20certainly%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20impact%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ffranz-beckenbauer%2Ft-67924159%5C%22%3EFranz%20Beckenbauer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20German%20footballing%20legend%20(11.09.45%20%E2%80%93%2008.01.24)%2C%20had%20on%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20a%20great%20player%2C%20positive%2C%20fast%20and%20always%20dangerous.%20He%20was%20the%20most%20dangerous%20player%20they%20had.%20He%20could%20do%20extraordinary%20things%20with%20his%20pace%2C%20control%20and%20ability.%E2%80%9D%20Those%20were%20the%20words%20with%20which%20the%20England%20and%20Manchester%20United%20legend%20Sir%20Bobby%20Charlton%20described%20Franz%20Beckenbauer%2C%20his%20great%20rival%20turned%20great%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20Beckenbauer%E2%80%99s%20skill%20as%20a%20central%20midfielder%20turned%20sweeper%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9CLibero%E2%80%9D%20role%20he%20is%20often%20credited%20with%20inventing%2C%20is%20unsurpassed%2C%20and%20he%20scaled%20heights%20that%20few%20others%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20game%20can%20or%20will%20ever%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20Bundesliga%20titles%2C%20four%20German%20Cups%2C%20three%20European%20Cups%2C%20one%20Cup%20Winners%E2%80%99%20Cup%2C%20three%20NASL%20titles%2C%20one%20European%20Championship%20and%20one%20World%20Cup%20as%20a%20player%20were%20followed%20by%20additional%20Bundesliga%2C%20Ligue%201%2C%20UEFA%20Cup%20and%20World%20Cup%20triumphs%20as%20a%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09152915%2F1500x500.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09152915%2F1500x500.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09152915%2F1500x500-300x100.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09152915%2F1500x500-1024x340.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692160%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22399%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFranz%20Beckenbauer%20(on%20the%20right).%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40beckenbauer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20individual%20honors%2C%20too%3A%20four%20times%20Beckenbauer%20was%20voted%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20footballer%20of%20the%20year%2C%20twice%20he%20won%20FIFA%E2%80%99s%20Ballon%20d%E2%80%99Or.%20No%20wonder%20Charlton%2C%20England%E2%80%99s%20best%20player%2C%20was%20ordered%20to%20man-mark%20the%20man%20they%20nicknamed%20%E2%80%9CDer%20Kaiser%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Emperor%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%201966%20World%20Cup%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Beckenbauer%E2%80%99s%20seemingly%20untouchable%20legacy%20was%20indeed%20tarnished%20in%20his%20later%20years%20as%20his%20role%20in%20the%20awarding%20of%20the%202006%20World%20Cup%20to%20Germany%20came%20under%20scrutiny.%20In%202016%2C%20FIFA%E2%80%99s%20Ethics%20Committee%20opened%20an%20investigation%20into%20a%20dubious%20payment%20of%20%E2%82%AC6.7%20million%20(%247.45m)%2C%20allegedly%20authorized%20with%20Beckenbauer%E2%80%99s%20knowledge%2C%20to%20influence%20votes%20on%20FIFA%E2%80%99s%20Executive%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuddenly%2C%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CSommerm%C3%A4rchen%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20the%20%E2%80%9Csummer%20fairy%20tale%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20historic%20World%20Cup%20summer%20became%20known%20%E2%80%93%20took%20on%20a%20darker%20hue%2C%20and%20Beckenbauer%20was%20one%20of%20the%20chief%20villains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20despite%20the%20allegations%2C%20Beckenbauer%20will%20be%20accorded%20a%20place%20in%20the%20pantheon%20of%20football%E2%80%99s%20greats%20alongside%20Johann%20Cruyff%2C%20Afredo%20di%20Stefano%2C%20Ferenc%20Puskas%2C%20George%20Best%2C%20Eus%C3%A9bio%2C%20Pele%20and%20Diego%20Maradona.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20boy%20from%20Bavaria%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeckenbauer%20was%20born%20on%20September%C2%A011%2C%201945%2C%20in%20the%20ruins%20of%20post-war%20Munich%20and%20began%20his%20career%20at%20local%20side%20SC%201906%20Munich%2C%20before%20moving%20to%20Bayern%20Munich%20aged%2013.%20Just%20five%20years%20later%20on%20June%206%2C%201964%2C%20the%2018-year-old%20Beckenbauer%20made%20his%20debut%20for%20Bayern%E2%80%99s%20first%20team%20against%20Stuttgarter%20Kickers%2C%20a%20game%20in%20which%20he%20also%20scored%20his%20first%20goal%20for%20the%20club%20as%20Bayern%20went%20on%20to%20win%20promotion%20to%20the%20Bundesliga.%20German%20and%20European%20Cup%20Winners%E2%80%99%20Cup%20successes%20followed%20before%20Beckenbauer%2C%20now%20captain%2C%20led%20Bayern%20to%20their%20first%20Bundesliga%20title%20%E2%80%93%20and%20only%20their%20second%20ever%20German%20championship%20%E2%80%93%20in%201969.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201970s%20would%20be%20Beckenbauer%E2%80%99s%20most%20successful%20decade%20as%20he%20led%20Bayern%20to%20three%20consecutive%20Bundesliga%20titles%20in%201972%2C%201973%20and%201974.%20The%20third%20was%20accompanied%20by%20the%20first%20of%20three%20consecutive%20European%20Cup%20wins%20%E2%80%93%20and%20a%20World%20Cup%20triumph%20on%20home%20turf%20as%20Beckenbauer%20captained%20West%20Germany%20to%20victory%20over%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09153153%2FClKIM0hUkAEV5yW.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09153153%2FClKIM0hUkAEV5yW.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09153153%2FClKIM0hUkAEV5yW-300x168.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09153153%2FClKIM0hUkAEV5yW-1024x573.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692163%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22671%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFranz%20Beckenbauer.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40beckenbauer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGerman%20captain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeckenbauer%E2%80%99s%20international%20career%20had%20begun%20nine%20years%20earlier%20in%20a%20World%20Cup%20qualifier%20against%20Sweden%20in%20Stockholm%20on%20September%2026%2C%201965%2C%20a%202-1%20win%20seeing%20Germany%20qualify%20for%20the%201966%20finals%20in%20England%2C%20where%20Germany%20lost%20in%20the%20final%20to%20the%20hosts.%20It%20was%20in%20that%20final%20that%20Beckenbauer%20and%20Charlton%20famously%20marked%20each%20other%20out%20of%20the%20game%2C%20such%20was%20the%20threat%20both%20posed%2C%20but%20Beckenbauer%20had%20still%20enjoyed%20a%20good%20tournament%20from%20an%20individual%20point%20of%20view%2C%20finishing%20third%20on%20the%20top-scorers%20list%20from%20a%20non-attacking%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20years%20later%20in%20Mexico%2C%20Germany%20took%20revenge%20on%20England%20as%20a%20stunning%20Beckenbauer%20goal%20inspired%20a%20comeback%20from%202-0%20down%20to%20knock%20out%20the%20reigning%20champions%20in%20the%20quarterfinal.%20Beckenbauer%20dislocated%20his%20shoulder%20in%20the%20semifinal%20defeat%20to%20Italy%20but%20continued%20to%20play%20on%20with%20his%20arm%20in%20a%20sling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20becoming%20captain%20of%20the%20national%20side%20in%201971%2C%20Beckenbauer%20led%20West%20Germany%20to%20victory%20in%20the%20European%20Championships%20in%201972%2C%20an%20achievement%20which%20saw%20him%20crowned%20European%20Footballer%20of%20the%20Year%20%E2%80%93%20only%20the%20second%20German%20to%20win%20the%20award%20after%20Gerd%20M%C3%BCller.%20When%20West%20Germany%20again%20reached%20the%20final%20four%20years%20later%2C%20this%20time%20losing%20on%20penalties%20to%20Czechoslovakia%2C%20Beckenbauer%20was%20named%20European%20Footballer%20of%20the%20Year%20for%20a%20second%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20finally%20lifting%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%201974%2C%20plus%20two%20more%20European%20Cups%20with%20Bayern%20in%201975%20and%201976%2C%20Beckenbauer%20became%20the%20first%20German%20player%20to%20move%20to%20the%20North%20American%20Soccer%20League%20(NASL)%20in%201977%20%E2%80%93%20although%2C%20with%20the%20German%20tax%20authorities%20on%20his%20case%2C%20the%20move%20also%20had%20private%20financial%20motives.%20Playing%20along%20Brazilian%20legend%20Pele%2C%20Beckenbauer%20won%20three%20NASL%20titles%20with%20the%20New%20York%20Cosmos%20and%20was%20inducted%20into%20the%20National%20Soccer%20Hall%20of%20Fame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeckenbauer%20moved%20back%20to%20Germany%20in%20May%201980%2C%20joining%20Hamburg%2C%20with%20whom%20he%20won%20a%20fifth%20Bundesliga%20title%20in%201982.%20Over%20the%20course%20of%20his%20career%2C%20Beckenbauer%20played%20424%20Bundesliga%20games%2C%20396%20for%20Bayern%20and%2028%20for%20HSV.%20He%20finally%20hung%20up%20his%20boots%20in%201983%20after%20one%20final%20season%20in%20New%20York%2C%20before%20embarking%20on%20a%20career%20in%20management%20when%20he%20took%20over%20the%20German%20national%20team%20following%20a%20group-stage%20exit%20at%20the%201984%20European%20Championships%20in%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeckenbauer%20the%20coach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20leading%20Germany%20to%20the%201986%20World%20Cup%20final%20against%20all%20expectations%2C%20Beckenbauer%20became%20only%20the%20second%20man%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%20both%20as%20a%20player%20and%20a%20coach%20when%20Germany%20lifted%20the%20trophy%20at%20Italia%20%E2%80%9990.%20In%202018%2C%20Didier%20Deschamps%20also%20achieved%20the%20feat%20when%20he%20led%20France%20to%20victory%20in%20Russia.%20In%20club%20management%2C%20Beckenbauer%20won%20a%20French%20Ligue%201%20title%20with%20Olympique%20Marseille%20in%201991%20and%20the%20Bundesliga%20with%20Bayern%20Munich%20in%201994%2C%20before%20becoming%20club%20president%20from%201994-2009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20his%20role%20at%20Bayern%2C%20Beckenbauer%20was%20also%20vice-president%20of%20the%20German%20Football%20Association%20(DFB)%20from%201998%20to%202010.%20It%20was%20in%20this%20capacity%20that%20he%20led%20the%20successful%20bid%20to%20host%20the%202006%20World%20Cup%2C%20a%20process%20which%20has%20since%20seen%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftime-runs-out-on-2006-world-cup-affair-trial%2Fa-53264879%5C%22%3EBeckenbauer%20embroiled%20in%20the%20corruption%20allegations%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20threaten%20to%20tarnish%20his%20legacy%20in%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnquiries%2C%20investigations%2C%20accusations%20%E2%80%93%20those%20discussions%20will%20rumble%20on.%20Today%2C%20memories%20are%20what%20matter%3B%20memories%20of%20a%20legendary%20figure%2C%20an%20iconic%20genius%2C%20a%20true%20giant%20of%20the%20game%2C%20the%20like%20of%20which%20we%20are%20unlikely%20to%20witness%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20who%20knows%3F%20Perhaps%20we%20will%20encounter%20Franz%20Anton%20Beckenbauer%20again%2C%20in%20some%20shape%20or%20form.%20He%20would%20like%20to%20think%20so%2C%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ffranz-beckenbauer-germanys-world-cup-winning-player-coach%2Fa-67921504%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20DW.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704796229000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09152605%2FCmvy8BWXgAA0-TG.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fgermanys-world-cup-winning-player-coach-franz-beckenbauer-passes-away%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20leading%20Germany%20to%20the%201986%20World%20Cup%20final%20against%20all%20expectations%2C%20Beckenbauer%20became%20only%20the%20second%20man%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%20both%20as%20a%20player%20and%20a%20coach.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fgermanys-world-cup-winning-player-coach-franz-beckenbauer-passes-away%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shraddha%20channels%20her%20inner%20Marathi%20Mulgi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704796200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fp