uctor%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20the%20program's%20website%20used%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finfo.maricopacorporate.com%2Fsemiconductor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epromise%20as%20much%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20this%20has%20since%20been%20removed.%20Early%20last%20year%2C%20industry%20job%20fairs%20were%20held%20on%20a%20monthly%20basis%2C%20with%20candidates%20having%20the%20opportunity%20to%20learn%20about%20career%20opportunities%20and%20meet%20recruiters.%20But%20these%20events%20have%20dried%20up%20%E2%80%94%20the%20last%20job%20fair%20was%20in%20June%2C%20and%20no%20others%20have%20been%20scheduled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Quick%20Start%20lab%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65395d2096f7540cd065a6a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20Quick%20Start%20students%20have%20struggled%20to%20find%20jobs%20in%20the%20semiconductor%20industry%20after%20the%20program.%20%3Cp%3EJacob%20Zinkula%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20students%20who%20were%20lucky%20enough%20to%20attend%20a%20job%20fair%20felt%20like%20they%20were%20flapping%20in%20the%20wind.%20A%20former%20Quick%20Start%20graduate%20told%20me%20that%20the%20job%20fair%20they%20attended%20in%20April%20left%20a%20lot%20to%20be%20desired.%20The%20graduate%20spoke%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20for%20fear%20of%20professional%20repercussions.%20Their%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%2C%20what%20happened%20was%20it%20was%2C%20like%2C%203%20%C2%BD%20hours%20of%20PowerPoints%2C%20and%20then%20the%20last%2030%20minutes%2C%20they%20were%20like%2C%20'OK%2C%20now%20networking%20time.%20Go%2C'%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%20a%20million%20people%20there%2C%20so%20even%20the%20people%20you%20wanted%20to%20talk%20to%2C%20you%20had%20to%20wait%20in%20a%20line.%20So%20it%20was%20a%20bit%20bungled.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20eventually%20landing%20an%20interview%20with%20a%20major%20semiconductor%20company%20last%20year%2C%20the%20graduate%20said%20they%20were%20told%20that%20the%20company's%20hiring%20freeze%20would%20likely%20prevent%20them%20from%20moving%20forward%20for%20at%20least%20a%20few%20months%20%E2%80%94%20they've%20since%20been%20told%20they're%20no%20longer%20being%20considered%20for%20the%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20really%20feel%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20we're%20dying%20for%20people.%20If%20you%20take%20this%20program%2C%20we'll%20help%20you%20get%20a%20good-paying%20job%2C'%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20in%20reference%20to%20semiconductor%20companies.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20that%20simple.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20eventually%20found%20work%20at%20the%20company%20through%20a%20contractor%20last%20year%2C%20they%20said%20they%20weren't%20optimistic%20about%20their%20near-term%20chances%20at%20direct%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20such%20a%20freaking%20long%20process%2C%20and%20now%20I'm%20actually%20having%20doubts%20whether%20I'm%20going%20to%20stick%20it%20out%20all%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20no%20longer%20promising%20interviews%20with%20semiconductor%20companies%2C%20Quick%20Start%20has%20taken%20other%20steps%20to%20moderate%20candidates'%20expectations.%20The%20program's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finfo.maricopacorporate.com%2Fsemiconductor%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSemiconductor%2520Technicians%2520help%2520manufacture%2520semiconductors%2Ccircuitry%2520and%2520change%2520conductive%2520properties.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%20says%20that%20hiring%20with%20its%20employment%20partners%20has%20%26quot%3Bslowed%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20doesn't%20%26quot%3Bknow%20when%20hiring%20will%20pick%20up%20again.%26quot%3B%20Program%20leaders%20hope%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20industry's%20hiring%20plans%20at%20the%20next%20advisory-board%20meeting%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20problem%20for%20the%20Quick%20Start%20program%20%E2%80%94%20and%20perhaps%20a%20contributor%20to%20graduates'%20hiring%20challenges%20%E2%80%94%20is%20the%20relatively%20short%20period%20of%20training.%20In%20the%20more%20difficult%20hiring%20environment%2C%20some%20of%20the%20chipmakers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20those%20who%20helped%20build%20the%20program%20%E2%80%94%20have%20started%20to%20question%20whether%20the%20training%20is%20sufficient%20to%20prepare%20graduates%20for%20jobs%20in%20the%20industry.%20Gabriela%20Cruz%20Thompson%2C%20Intel's%20director%20of%20university%20research%20collaboration%2C%20said%20late%20in%202023%20that%20the%20company%20was%20evaluating%20whether%20the%20Quick%20Start%20graduates%20were%20being%20set%20up%20for%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20asking%20ourselves%20and%20asking%20the%20managers%20of%20those%20people%20that%20got%20hired%20whether%20this%20training%20is%20enough%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20unfair%20to%20them%20to%20hire%20them%20and%20then%20they%20don't%20deliver%20in%20the%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20training%20is%20deemed%20insufficient%2C%20Maricopa%20County%20may%20consider%20adopting%20something%20closer%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theregister.com%2F2023%2F09%2F25%2Fintel_semiconductor_course%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eone-year%20training%20program%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Intel%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20rolling%20out%20with%20Ohio%20community%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hiring%20slowdown%2C%20and%20the%20reconsideration%20of%20the%20program's%20status%20as%20an%20adequate%20training%20ground%2C%20has%20forced%20Quick%20Start%20leaders%20to%20consider%20reducing%20enrollment%20%E2%80%94%20even%20as%20demand%20for%20the%20training%20persists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20slow%20down%20our%20pipeline%20so%20that%20we're%20not%20putting%20out%20more%20people%20with%20absolutely%20no%20possibility%20of%20employment%2C%26quot%3B%20Palmer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnless%20circumstances%20change%20soon%2C%20she%20said%20the%20program%20would%20likely%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20classes%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20set%20to%20be%2014%20this%20spring%20across%20the%20three%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHurdles%20abound%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20short-term%20economics%2C%20Palmer%20believes%20there%20are%20two%20reasons%20semiconductor%20companies%20have%20been%20slow%20to%20hire%2C%20she%20said.%20First%2C%20they're%20waiting%20to%20see%20how%20CHIPS%20Act%20funding%20gets%20doled%20out.%20In%20December%2C%20nearly%201%20%C2%BD%20years%20after%20the%20legislation%20was%20signed%20into%20law%2C%20the%20first%20CHIPS%20Act%20grant%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-12-11%2Fus-awards-35-million-to-defense-firm-bae-in-first-chips-grant%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eannounced%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20waiting%20period%20has%20slowed%20the%20plans%20of%20companies%20such%20as%20TSMC%2C%20which%20is%20seeking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-taiwan-semiconductor-phoenix-arizona-factory-chipmaker-job-qualification-debate-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebillions%20of%20dollars%20of%20US%20subsidies%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20know%20how%20much%20money%20they're%20going%20to%20get%20and%20when%20they're%20going%20to%20get%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Palmer%20said%20of%20semiconductor%20companies%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20being%20told%20by%20industry%20that%20after%20CHIPS%20money%20lands%2C%20the%20comfort%20of%20planning%20for%20the%20future%20will%20open%20permanent%20hires.%26quot%3B%20If%20Biden%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftrump-leads-biden-in-swing-states-voters-not-fans-of-bidenomics-here-s-what-a-new-2024-election-poll-reveals-1032722495%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eloses%20the%20presidency%20this%20year%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Palmer%20said%2C%20the%20uncertainty%20over%20funding%20may%20further%20curtail%20hiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20while%20many%20chip%20factories%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-building-factories-census-data-chips-act-inflation-reduction-act-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebeing%20built%20across%20the%20US%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20workers%20can't%20staff%20a%20fabrication%20plant%20until%20it's%20built.%20Construction%20delays%20haven't%20helped%20matters.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-12-26%2Fsamsung-delays-production-at-new-us-factory-to-2025-daily-says%3FleadSource%3Duverify%2520wall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESamsung%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20TSMC%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20have%20each%20postponed%20chip%20production%20from%202024%20to%202025%20%E2%80%94%20the%20latter%20said%20it%20was%20due%20in%20part%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-taiwan-semiconductor-phoenix-arizona-factory-chipmaker-job-qualification-debate-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eshortage%20of%20skilled%20construction%20workers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20factors%20could%20also%20slow%20construction.%20In%20December%2C%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Gina%20Raimondo%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-12-12%2Fraimondo-warns-us-chips-push-faces-long-delays-in-permit-process%3FleadSource%3Duverify%2520wall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eenvironmental-review%20requirements%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20force%20the%20construction%20of%20some%20chip%20projects%20to%20be%20halted%20for%20%26quot%3Bup%20to%20years.%26quot%3B%20Congressional%20efforts%20to%20exempt%20chip%20companies%20from%20some%20of%20these%20reviews%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-12-12%2Fraimondo-warns-us-chips-push-faces-long-delays-in-permit-process%3FleadSource%3Duverify%2520wall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehave%20stalled%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20hiring%20mess%20has%20been%20incredibly%20frustrating%20for%20some%20Quick%20Start%20students%2C%20given%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-china-tech-war-computer-chips-semiconductor-plants-costing-americans-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elong-term%20outlook%20for%20the%20industry%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20many%20students%20in%20the%20class%20I%20visited%20seemed%20to%20view%20Quick%20Start%20as%20a%20valuable%20opportunity.%20In%20the%20years%20ahead%2C%20the%20artificial-intelligence%20boom%20could%20further%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.deloitte.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Finsights%2Findustry%2Ftechnology%2Ftechnology-media-and-telecom-predictions%2F2024%2Fgenerative-ai-chip-market-to-reach-40-billion-in-2024.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eboost%20the%20demand%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20chips%20and%20create%20more%20jobs%20in%20the%20semiconductor%20industry.%20But%20for%20recent%20Quick%20Start%20graduates%2C%20who%20are%20eager%20for%20employment%20now%2C%20promises%20of%20future%20hiring%20may%20offer%20little%20peace%20of%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20I%20followed%20up%20with%20Gardner%2C%20the%20fast-food%20worker%20who%20turned%20to%20Quick%20Start%2C%20to%20learn%20how%20his%20job%20search%20was%20going.%20He%20said%20he'd%20tried%20looking%20for%20roles%20but%20that%20more%20than%20two%20months%20later%2C%20he%20still%20hadn't%20landed%20a%20job%20in%20the%20semiconductor%20industry.%20Gardner%20told%20me%20that%20it%20was