ades-taiwan-it-would-cost-world-economy-10-trillion%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20Economics%3C%2Fa%3E%20analysis%20published%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20GDP%20could%20take%20a%206.7%25%20hit%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20conflict%20if%20Washington%20gets%20drawn%20into%20the%20war%2C%20Bloomberg%20forecasts.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20a%20Chinese%20blockade%20of%20the%20island%20%E2%80%94%20a%20major%20semiconductor%20chip%20producer%20%E2%80%94%20the%20US%20could%20see%203.3%25%20shaved%20off%20its%20GDP%20in%20the%20first%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20Bloomberg's%20forecast%2C%20the%20economic%20impact%20in%20both%20scenarios%20would%20be%20worse%20than%20in%202020%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fus%2Fus-gdp-revised-down-every-first-quarter-2020-2022-2023-09-28%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20GDP%3C%2Fa%3E%20contracted%202.2%25%20due%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20impact%20on%20the%20US%20economy%20pales%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20impact%20on%20other%20economies%2C%20Bloomberg%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20a%20war%20over%20Taiwan%20could%20hit%20the%20world's%20economy%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20%2410%20trillion%20%E2%80%94%20or%20about%2010%25%20of%20global%20GDP%20%E2%80%94%20Bloomberg%20forecasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaiwan%20could%20see%2040%25%20shaved%20off%20its%20GDP%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20a%20war%20while%20China's%20GDP%20could%20tank%2016.7%25%2C%20Bloomberg%20predicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20countries%20most%20affected%20by%20war%20over%20Taiwan%20include%20South%20Korea%20and%20Japan%2C%20which%20could%20see%20their%20growth%20contract%20by%2023.3%25%20and%2013.5%25%20respectively%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20Bloomberg%20predicts.%20Southeast%20Asia's%20GDP%20as%20a%20region%20could%20tank%20by%2020.1%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%20Economics'%20analysis%20is%20based%20on%20geopolitical%20considerations%20and%20economic%20modeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20came%20days%20ahead%20of%20Taiwan's%20general%20and%20presidential%20elections%2C%20which%20are%20slated%20to%20be%20held%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaiwan's%20elections%20are%20closely%20watched%20because%20China%20claims%20the%20self-ruled%20island%20%E2%80%94%20a%20semiconductor%20powerhouse%20%E2%80%94%20as%20its%20own%20territory.%20There%20are%20fears%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-would-happen-china-invades-taiwan-economy-military-politics-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EChinese%20invasion%20of%20Taiwan%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%20global%20economy%20and%20regional%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20doesn't%20appear%20as%20if%20China%20is%20set%20to%20invade%20Taiwan%20any%20time%20soon%2C%20Beijing%20has%20been%20ramping%20up%20military%20drills%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20On%20New%20Year's%20Eve%2C%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fchina-calls-taiwan-president-frontrunner-destroyer-peace-2023-12-31%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Breunification%26quot%3B%20with%20Taiwan%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20inevitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETensions%20between%20China%20and%20Taiwan%20could%20rise%20if%20presidential%20frontrunner%20William%20Lai%20Ching-te%20from%20the%20ruling%20Democratic%20Progressive%20Party%2C%20or%20DPP%2C%20win%20the%20presidential%20race.%20Beijing%20views%20Lai%20as%20a%20separatist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20Lai%20wins%2C%20China%20could%20step%20up%20retaliatory%20measures%20such%20as%20import%20bans%20and%20intensify%20military%20drills%2C%20Vishnu%20Varathan%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Asia%20economics%20and%20strategy%20at%20Mizuho%20Bank%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20DPP%20win%20may%20not%20be%20exactly%20business%20as%20usual%20as%20Beijing%20is%20likely%20to%20continue%20viewing%20Lai%20as%20an%20obstacle%20towards%20reunification%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Varathan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaiwan-war-impact-us-economic-growth-first-year-china-chips-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704794089000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659ce19bec62ab5daf81c540%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaiwan-war-impact-us-economic-growth-first-year-china-chips-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20war%20over%20Taiwan%20would%20hit%20the%20world%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20%2410%20trillion%2C%20Bloomberg%20forecasts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaiwan-war-impact-us-economic-growth-first-year-china-chips-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Is%20Still%20Angry%20-%20Congress%20Must%20Read%20The%20Signs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJanata%20Dal%20United%20(JDU)%20spokesperson%20KC%20Tyagi's%20statement%20on%208%20January%20in%20the%20Indian%20Express%20is%20the%20clue%20that%20there%20are%20serious%20issues%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20is%20not%20happy.%20Tyagi%20is%20an%20experienced%20political%20leader.%20He%20is%20not%20a%20loose%20cannon.%20He%20is%20known%20in%20political%20circles%20for%20his%20measured%20statements.%20Therefore%2C%20his%20frontal%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%20must%20be%20taken%20seriously.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20way%20the%20Congress%20chief%20responded%20to%20media%20questions%20on%20Saturday%20on%20this%20(convenor%20question)%20did%20not%20go%20down%20well%20with%20us.%20We%20are%20running%20out%20of%20time%20and%20ideas.%20We%20still%20have%20time%20to%20catch%20up.%20But%20it%20is%20Congress%20that%20has%20to%20show%20urgency%20to%20see%20a%20vibrant%20INDIA%20bloc.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETyagi%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20has%20embarked%20on%20its%20Yatra.%20Rather%2C%20it%20should%20have%20been%20an%20INDIA%20Yatra%20in%20which%20all%20top%20leaders%20could%20have%20participated.%20The%20Congress%20did%20not%20consult%20any%20of%20its%20allies%20before%20charting%20its%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%20We%20welcome%20the%20Yatra.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20good%20time%20to%20start%20it.%20India%20is%20still%20confused.%20What%20if%20parliamentary%20elections%20are%20announced%20soon%20after%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20opening%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20understood%20that%20he%20can't%20give%20a%20statement%20of%20this%20nature%20without%20consulting%20party%20boss%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20Tyagi%20has%20targeted%20two%20of%20the%20top%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress.%20He%20has%20attacked%20party%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20INDIA%20convenor%2C%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20on%20his%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%20He%20has%20effectively%20suggested%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20failed%20to%20lead%20INDIA%2C%20as%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20is%20not%20really%20showing%20urgency%20in%20crafting%20a%20counter-narrative%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Hindutva%20pitch.%20He%20has%20also%20hinted%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20taking%20decisions%20unilaterally%20without%20consulting%20allies.%20These%20charges%20are%20serious%2C%20and%20if%20not%20addressed%20immediately%2C%20can%20precipitate%20a%20bigger%20crisis%20in%20the%20opposition%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20common%20knowledge%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar%20is%20extremely%20ambitious%20and%20that%20he%20is%20eyeing%20the%20top%20job%20-%20prime%20ministership%20-%20and%20to%20that%20end%2C%20becoming%20convenor%20would%20be%20the%20first%20step.%20When%20he%20walked%20away%20from%20the%20NDA%20and%20joined%20hands%20with%20Lalu%20Yadav%2C%20it%20was%20assumed%20that%20in%20due%20course%20he%20would%20hand%20over%20the%20baton%20in%20Bihar%20to%20deputy%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20and%20move%20on%20to%20a%20bigger%20role%20in%20national%20politics.%20It%20was%20widely%20speculated%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar%20could%20be%20the%20ideal%20candidate%20to%20challenge%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20a%20good%20choice%20for%20INDIA's%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20has%20always%20fancied%20his%20credentials%20for%20the%20top%20job.%20Like%20Modi%2C%20he%20has%20been%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20a%20state%20for%20more%20than%2010%20years.%20Like%20Modi%2C%20he%20belongs%20to%20the%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes)%20community.%20Nitish%20Kumar%20is%20a%20Kurmi.%20Kurmis%20are%20the%20most%20powerful%20and%20politically%20savvy%20caste%20within%20the%20OBC%20community%20after%20Yadavs%20in%20north%20India.%20His%20presence%20can%20restrict%20the%20flow%20of%20OBCs%20towards%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20can%20substantially%20weaken%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20the%20Hindi-speaking%20belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20MK%20Stalin%20and%20Kharge%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20comes%20from%20the%20Hindi%20belt.%20This%20is%20the%20core%20area%20for%20the%20BJP.%20Here%20the%20BJP%20has%20won%20more%20than%2090%20per%20cent%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20election.%20If%20Modi%20has%20to%20be%20stopped%20from%20becoming%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20the%20third%20time%2C%20then%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20to%20win%20major%20seats%20in%20Hindi-speaking%20states.%20Here%20the%20Congress%20is%20involved%20in%20a%20direct%20fight%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20if%20Nitish%20Kumar%20is%20projected%20as%20presumptive%20prime%20minister%2C%20a%20large%20section%20of%20OBC%20voters%20can%20be%20swayed%20towards%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20parties%20like%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20what%20is%20the%20problem%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20this%20-%20even%20within%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20is%20not%20trusted%20so%20much.%20His%20moves%20are%20viewed%20with%20suspicion.%20Even%20his%20old%20friend%20Lalu%20Yadav%20is%20often%20hard-pressed%20to%20predict%20his%20next%20political%20move.%20The%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20also%20perceived%20to%20be%20extremely%20self-centred%20and%20very%20secretive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20problem%20is%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20commitment%20to%20secularism%20is%20doubtful.%20Ideologically%2C%20he%20is%20a%20socialist%20but%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20political%20power%2C%20he%20has%20never%20had%20any%20qualms%20about%20dallying%20with%20the%20BJP.%20In%20fact%2C%20since%20his%20exit%20from%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20he%20has%20spent%20more%20time%20with%20the%20BJP%20than%20his%20old%20socialist%20friends.%20He%20was%20a%20minister%20in%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee's%20cabinet.%20Then%20he%20became%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Bihar%20with%20the%20BJP's%20help%20and%20continued%20till%202014.%20Once%20Modi%20became%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20he%20ditched%20the%20BJP%20and%20joined%20hands%20with%20friend-turned-rival%20Lalu%20Yadav.%20After%20they%20won%20the%20Bihar%20election%20together%2C%20he%20swapped%20alliances%20again%2C%20dumping%20the%20RJD%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%202017.%20Then%20another%20somersault%20in%202022%20and%20a%20reunion%20with%20RJD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20history%2C%20when%20Nitish%20forced%20Lalan%20Singh%20to%20resign%20as%20national%20party%20chief%20of%20the%20JDU%20and%20took%20his%20place%2C%20many%20assumed%20it%20was%20a%20precursor%20to%20another%20switcheroo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20without%20reason%20that%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20meeting%20on%20December%2019%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20proposed%20that%20Kharge%20should%20be%20projected%20as%20PM%20face.%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20immediately%20seconded%20that%20proposal.%20Mamata%20and%20Kejriwal%20both%20harbour%20prime%20ministerial%20ambitions.%20Their%20proposal%20was%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20scuttle%20Nitish's%20chances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee's%20move%20was%20curious.%20Just%20a%20day%20before%20the%20meeting%2C%20she%20had%20said%20INDIA%20should%20not%20project%20anyone%20as%20PM%20candidate%20for%20the%202024%20elections.%20The%20very%20next%20day%2C%20she%20pulled%20a%20surprise.%20I%20was%20told%20by%20a%20senior%20INDIA%20bloc%20leader%20that%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20not%20very%20enthusiastic%20about%20Nitish%20Kumar%20becoming%20convenor.%20I%20was%20told%20even%20Stalin%20had%20reservations%2C%20though%20the%20Congress%20was%20on%20board%20with%20making%20him%20INDIA%20convenor.%20The%20Congress%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20working%20on%20building%20consensus%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20name%20could%20be%20announced%20soon%2C%20I%20am%20told.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20understood%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar%20is%20upset.%20After%20the%20INDIA%20meeting%2C%20both%20Kharge%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20spoke%20to%20the%20JDU%20leader%2C%20presumably%20to%20mollify%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Tyagi's%20outburst%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20Nitish%20is%20still%20upset.%20The%20general%20election%20is%20less%20than%20three%20months%20away.%20The%20BJP%20is%20already%20in%20election%20mode%20(is%20it%20ever%20off%3F)%20and%20has%20prepared%20to%20ride%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20wave.%20The%20BJP%20is%20also%20in%20high%20spirits%20after%20winning%20three%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20not%20seen%20as%20united%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20taken%20seriously%20as%20a%20challenger.%20The%20opposition%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20has%20to%20understand%20that%20it%20is%20up%20against%20the%20most%20dynamic%20election%20machine%20in%20independent%20India.%20It%20will%20require%20special%20talent%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%20The%20sooner%20they%20understand%20this%2C%20the%20better%20it%20will%20be.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20battle%20will%20be%20lost%20long%20before%20it%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKC%20Tyagi's%20outburst%20is%20a%20warning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20Editor%2C%20satyahindi.com.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704794040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fqfg927l8_cm-nitish-kumar-_625x300_01_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnitish-kumar-is-still-angry-congress-must-read-the-signs-4829141%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Janata%20Dal%20United%20(JDU)%20spokesperson%20KC%20Tyagi's%20statement%20on%208%20January%20in%20the%20Indian%20Express%20is%20the%20clue%20that%20there%20are%20serious%20issues%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20is%20not%20happy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnitish-kumar-is-still-angry-congress-must-read-the-signs-4829141%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnitish-kumar-is-still-angry-congress-must-read-the-signs-4829141%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnitish-kumar-is-still-angry-congress-must-read-the-signs-4829141%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20satellite%20launch%20triggers%20air%20raid%20alert%20in%20Taiwan%20ahead%20of%20election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704793700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F17039%2Fproduction%2F_132256249_gettyimages-1885828449.jpg%22%2C%22originI