%20is%20a%20dream%3B%20life%20passes%20and%20people%20are%20not%20able%20to%20win%20this%20award.%20I%20am%20happy%20that%20I%20have%20been%20nominated%20for%20this%20award.%20It%20is%20like%20a%20dream%20for%20me%20to%20get%20this%20award%20because%20my%20whole%20life%20I%20have%20seen%20many%20people%20receiving%20this%20award%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohammed%20Shami%20had%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPara-archer%20Sheetal%20Devi%20Aditi%20Swami%2C%20steeplechaser%20Parul%20Chaudhary%2C%20shooter%20Aishwary%20Pratap%20Singh%20Tomar%20and%20U20%20World%20Champion%20wrestler%20Antim%20Panghal%20have%20received%20the%20award%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheetal%20won%20three%20medals%20in%20last%20year's%20Para%20Asian%20Games%2C%20which%20included%20a%20women's%20team%20silver%2C%20a%20mixed%20team%20gold%2C%20and%20gold%20in%20the%20women's%20singles%20compound%20open%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20women's%20singles%20event%2C%20Sheetal%20showcased%20a%20stupendous%20performance%20and%20defeated%20Singapore's%20Alim%20Nur%20Syahidah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20closely%20fought%20contest%20as%20Alim%20Nur%2C%20with%20her%20precision%2C%20took%20a%20point%20lead%20in%20the%20first%20three%20sets.%20She%20enjoyed%20a%20three-point%20lead%20after%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20first%20three%20sets%2C%20with%20the%20final%20two%20sets%20remaining.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheetal%20produced%20back-to-back%20perfect%20scores%20to%20clinch%20the%20game%2C%20with%20Alim%20Nur%20missing%20the%20mark%20on%20a%20couple%20of%20shots.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20she%20emerged%20victorious%20with%20an%20overall%20score%20of%20144-142.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20archers%20bagged%20nine%20medals%20including%20five%20gold%20medals.%20World%20No.%209%2C%20Ojas%20Pravin%20won%20two%20gold%20medals%20while%20Jyothi%20Surekha%20won%20three%20medals%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOjas%20faced%20Abhishek%20Verma%20in%20the%20final%20of%20the%20men's%20compound%20archery%20and%20defeated%20Abhishek%20to%20bag%20the%20gold%20medal%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20149-147.Ojas%20won%20second%20gold%20with%20Jyothi%20Surekha%20in%20the%20mixed%20team%20compound%20archery%20event%20after%20defeating%20South%20Korea's%20Chaewon%20So%20and%20Jaehoon%20Joo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EList%20of%20Arjun%20Awardees%3A%20Mohammed%20Shami%20(cricket)%2C%20Ajay%20Reddy%20(blind%20cricket)%20Ojas%20Pravin%20Deotale%20(archery)%2C%20Aditi%20Gopichand%20Swami%20(archery)%2C%20Sheetal%20Devi%20(para%20archery)%2C%20Parul%20Chaudhary%20and%20Murali%20Sreeshankar%20(athletics)%2C%20Mohd%20Hussamuddin%20(boxing)%2C%20R%20Vaishali%20(chess)%2C%20Divyakriti%20Singh%20and%20Anush%20Agarwalla%20(equestrian)%2C%20Diksha%20Dagar%20(golf)%2C%20Krishan%20Bahadur%20Pathak%20(hockey)%2C%20Sushila%20Chanu%20(hockey)%2C%20Pinky%20(lawn%20ball)%2C%20Aishwary%20Pratap%20Singh%20Tomar%20(shooting)%2C%20Antim%20Panghal%20(wrestling)%2C%20Ayhika%20Mukherjee%20(table%20tennis).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704793440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Faoccnss8_shami_625x300_09_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fthe-proud-moment-mohammed-shami-was-conferred-with-arjuna-award-by-president-murmu-watch-4828143%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohammed%20Shami%20ended%20as%20the%20leading%20wicket-taker%20in%20last%20year's%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20in%20India%20with%2024%20scalps%20and%20broke%20several%20records.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fthe-proud-moment-mohammed-shami-was-conferred-with-arjuna-award-by-president-murmu-watch-4828143%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fthe-proud-moment-mohammed-shami-was-conferred-with-arjuna-award-by-president-murmu-watch-4828143%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fthe-proud-moment-