%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20email%2C%20Ms%20Ransome%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20also%20have%20other%20photos%20(sic)%20of%20the%20Epstein%20girls%20and%20I%2C%20whilst%20on%20the%20Island%20including%20a%20couple%20of%20pictures%20of%20me%20with%20Sergey%20Brin%20and%20his%20then%20finance%20Anne%20Wojcicki%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20met%20the%20pair%20when%20they%20visited%20the%20Island%20for%20the%20day%20as%20Sergey%20wanted%20to%20try%20out%20his%20new%20kitesurfing%20equipment%20as%20he%20had%20only%20just%20started%20surfing%20and%20was%20very%20eager%20to%20try%20out%20his%20new%20equipment%20with%20us%20girls%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESergey%20Brin%20separated%20from%20Anne%20Wojcicki%20in%202015%20after%20eight%20years%20of%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20to%20Maureen%20Callahan%2C%20Ms%20Ransome%20also%20claimed%20that%20former%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20%E2%80%9Csexual%20relations%E2%80%9D%20with%20her%20friend.%20However%2C%20she%20later%20took%20back%20all%20the%20allegations%20in%20an%20email%20dated%20October%2023%2C%202016%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20retract%20everything%20I%20have%20said%20to%20you%20and%20walk%20away%20from%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20Epstein%20brought%20several%20rich%20clients%20to%20JPMorgan%20Chase%2C%20which%20included%20Sergey%20Brin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20court%20documents%2C%20the%20Google%20co-founder%20was%20one%20of%20its%20biggest%20clients%20having%20invested%20worth%20more%20than%20%244%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBrin%20became%20a%20client%20of%20JPMorgan's%20San%20Francisco%20Private%20Bank%20in%202004%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20filings%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEpstein%2C%20convicted%20paedophile%20and%20financier%2C%20died%20in%20jail%20on%20August%2010%2C%202019%2C%20b