oard%20Flight%201282%20when%20the%20plane%20lost%20its%20door%2016%2C000%20feet%20in%20the%20air.%20In%20a%20TikTok%20video%2C%20Ms%20Vu%20explained%20how%20she%20felt%20the%20entire%20plane%20drop%20and%20feared%20she%20wouldn't%20survive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20masks%20r%20down.%20I%20am%20so%20scared%20right%20now...Please%20pray%20for%20me.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20die%2C''%20she%20texted%20her%20parents%2C%20believing%20they%20could%20have%20been%20her%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20she%20recalled%2C%20''I%20woke%20up%20to%20the%20plane%20just%20falling%20and%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20not%20just%20normal%20turbulence%20because%20the%20masks%20came%20down%2C%20and%20that's%20when%20the%20panic%20started%20to%20set%20in.%C2%A0You%20just%20think%20it's%20never%20going%20to%20happen%20to%20you%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20it%20did%20happen%20to%20me.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-t%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bn%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BblueLinks%26quot%3B%7D%5C%22%3E''I'm%20home%20now%2C%20it's%20OK.%20I'm%20definitely%20still%20shaken%20up%2C''%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-t%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bn%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BblueLinks%26quot%3B%7D%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20so%20grateful%20for%20the%20ladies%20sat%20next%20to%20me...%20they%20were%20so%20sweet%20at%20calming%20me%20down%2C%20and%20the%20flight%20attendants%20were%20giving%20oxygen%20tanks%20to%20those%20who%20needed%20it%20more.%20But%20I%20was%20freaking%20out%20because%20my%20bag%20wouldn't%20inflate%20-%20and%20that's%20literally%20what%20they%20tell%20you%20in%20the%20safety%20thing%2C%20like%20don't%20worry%20you're%20still%20getting%20airflow%20when%20you're%20in%20fight%20or%20flight%20you're%20not%20thinking%20about%20that''%2C%20she%20further%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Vu%20also%20spoke%20to%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Fvideos%2Fworld%2F2024%2F01%2F06%2Fexp-alaska-airlines-plane-window-emma-vu-intv-010603aseg1-cnni