nseen-moments-of-the-bride-and-her-mother-steal-the-spotlight%2Farticleshow%2F106662483.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blog%3A%20A%20Common%20Road%20Tax%20For%20Entire%20Nation%20Coming%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20is%20seriously%20studying%20if%20it%20could%20implement%20this%20year%20a%20pathbreaking%20idea%20of%20a%20common%20road%20tax%20for%20the%20whole%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20work%2C%20if%20the%20Centre%20can%20convince%20the%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20NDA%20government%20had%20mooted%20in%202016%20but%20failed%20to%20implement%20because%20of%20strong%20resistance%20from%20a%20number%20of%20states%2C%20especially%20those%20ruled%20by%20the%20opposition%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20effect%20to%20revenues%20outside%20GST%20has%20been%20a%20contentious%20issue%20amongst%20states%20averse%20to%20such%20reforms%20as%20it%20would%20take%20a%20hit%20on%20their%20revenues.%20States%20believe%20and%20claim%20that%20road%20taxes%20differ%20in%20their%20states%20depending%20on%20levels%20of%20development%20and%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20states.%20States%2C%20especially%20the%20likes%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Kerala%20have%20the%20highest%20taxation%20rates%20and%20feel%20they%20are%20justified%20when%20compared%20to%20laggard%20states.%20And%20after%20the%20GST%20experience%20around%20compensation%20and%20share%2C%20some%20states%20hold%20apprehensions%20that%20such%20moves%20will%20further%20hit%20their%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20contentious%20issues%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20states%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20taxation%20revolve%20around%20fuel%2C%20alcohol%2C%20land%20registery%20and%20vehicle%20registrations.%20Interestingly%2C%20it%20was%20in%202018%20when%20a%20Group%20of%20Ministers%20(GoM)%20on%20transport%20had%20recommended%20a%20uniform%20road%20tax%20structure%20for%20vehicles%20across%20states%20and%20that%20the%20tax%20be%20charged%20based%20on%20the%20invoice%20price%20of%20a%20vehicle.%20But%20the%20states%20still%20did%20not%20agree%2C%20they%20argued%20transportation%20is%20a%20state%20subject%20and%20the%20prerogative%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20things%20have%20changed%20politically%20for%20the%20NDA%20government%2C%20which%20recently%20won%20some%20crucial%20elections%20in%20the%20states.%20Now%2C%20the%20government%20may%20come%20out%20with%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20subject%20submitted%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20(MoRTH)%20by%20IndiaTech%2C%20a%20top%20think%20tank%20that%20works%20to%20develop%20internet%20commerce%20ecosystem%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20reliably%20learnt%20that%20the%20government%20wants%20prevention%20of%20tax%20evasion%20and%20completely%20stop%20multiplicity%20of%20road%20taxes.%20The%20move%2C%20feels%20the%20government%2C%20will%20promote%20simplicity%20of%20transfers%2C%20payments%20and%20refunds%2C%20and%20removing%20what%20has%20been%20a%20major%20economic%20roadblock%20in%20transferring%2C%20buying%20and%20selling%20of%20pre-registered%20vehicles.%20The%20move%2C%20feels%20the%20government%2C%20will%20also%20bring%20about%20a%20much-needed%20ease%20of%20owning%20and%20disposing%20of%20vehicles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%2C%20temporarily%20christened%20%3Cem%3EOne%20Bharat%2C%20One%20Road%20Tax%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20a%20model%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20implement%20as%20a%20uniform%20road%20taxation%20regime%20will%20bring%20about%20a%20unified%20framework%2C%20making%20the%20public%20understand%20and%20comply%20with%20simplified%20road%20tax%20regulations%2C%20irrespective%20of%20where%20they%20are%20living%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20move%2C%20says%20the%20white%20paper%2C%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20alleviate%20citizens%20of%20cumbersome%20compliances%2C%20open%20avenues%20for%20businesses%20to%20efficiently%20trade%20used%20vehicles%2C%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20government's%20efforts%20to%20digitally%20transform%20the%20nation%20bear%20fruit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EOne%20Bharat%2C%20One%20Road%20Tax%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20disincentivize%20tax%20evasion%2C%20remove%20barriers%20in%20the%20used%20vehicle%20industry%2C%20and%20make%20inter-state%20sales%20of%20pre-owned%20vehicles%20easier%2C%26quot%3B%20Rameesh%20Kailasam%2C%20CEO%20and%20President%2C%20IndiaTech%2C%20has%20been%20quoted%20in%20the%20white%20paper%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20each%20state%20follows%20its%20own%20formula%20for%20arriving%20at%20road%20tax%2C%20leading%20to%20varied%20prices%20of%20the%20same%20model%20of%20vehicle%20in%20different%20states.%20Consider%20this%20one.%20The%20rate%20of%20road%20tax%20varies%20from%202%20to%2018%20percent%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20vehicle%20in%20different%20states.%20Simply%20put%2C%20on-road%20prices%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20strikingly%20different%20from%20state%20to%20state%20for%20the%20same%20model.%20So%20it%20is%20fairly%20common%20to%20have%20buyers%20purchasing%20cars%20in%20another%20state%2C%20rather%20than%20their%20state%20of%20domicile%20or%20residence%2C%20due%20to%20lower%20road%20tax%20in%20those%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20what%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20Paper%20makes%20a%20number%20of%20recommendations%20on%20reforms%20needed%20for%20ease%20of%20owning%20and%20disposing%20of%20vehicles.%20It%20calls%20for%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20national%20digital%20RTOs'%20dashboard%2C%20standardization%20and%20digitisation%20of%20Registration%20Certificates%20(RCs)%20and%20achieving%20100%25%20digitisation%20in%20the%20area%20of%20challans%20to%20improve%20revenue%20collection%20and%20accountability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20it%20is%20reliably%20learnt%2C%20is%20in%20sync%20with%20almost%20all%20the%20recommendations%20made%20in%20the%20White%20Paper.%20The%20government%20wants%20to%20remove%20bottlenecks%20faced%20by%20the%20used%20vehicles%20market%2C%20including%20start-ups%20engaged%20in%20the%20sale%20of%20pre-owned%20vehicles.%20These%20include%20an%20overhaul%20of%20the%20cumbersome%20inter-state%20vehicle%20registration%20process%20that%20currently%20involves%20physical%20verification%20and%20physical%20filing.%20The%20government%20wants%20a%20simpler%20format%20akin%20to%20first%20sales%20of%20cars%20and%20'vehicle%20evaluation'%20by%20the%20pre-owned%20vehicle%20dealer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20also%20contemplating%20controlled%20access%20to%20the%20national%20vehicle%20registry%20database%20to%20licensed%20used%20car%20dealers%20(UCDs)%2C%20insurance%20companies%2C%20scrap%20dealers%2C%20and%20automotive%20workshop%20organizers.%20This%20would%20help%20in%20verifying%20the%20hypothecation%20details%20when%20a%20vehicle%20is%20being%20sold%20so%20that%20buyers%20are%20aware%20of%20any%20pre-existing%20hypothecation%20or%20other%20charges.%20It%20will%20be%20easier%20to%20check%20blacklisted%20vehicles.%20This%20would%20further%20ease%20the%20cumbersome%20system%20of%20owning%20and%20disposing%20of%20vehicles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20also%20advocates%20that%20Form%2029C%20is%20amended%20to%20include%20the%20transfer%20of%20deemed%20ownership%20from%20one%20registered%20used%20car%20dealer%20to%20another%20registered%20dealer%20since%20a%20common%20practice%20in%20the%20industry%20is%20the%20transfer%20of%20vehicles%20from%20one%20dealer%20to%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20paper%20advocates%20a%20centralised%20registration%20for%20Used%20Car%20Dealers%20(UCDs)%20instead%20of%20the%20current%20law%20where%20authorization%20of%20dealers%20of%20registered%20vehicles%20can%20be%20made%20only%20to%20the%20registering%20authority%20under%20whose%20jurisdiction%20they%20have%20their%20business.%20This%20move%20is%20also%20important%2C%20else%20pre-owned%20car%20startups%20having%20pan-India%20business%20will%20end%20up%20registering%20in%20each%20and%20every%20RTO%20and%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shantanu%20Guha%20Ray%20is%20the%20Asia%20Editor%20of%20Central%20European%20News%2C%20UK.%20His%20book%20on%20coal%2C%20Black%20Harvest%2C%20will%20hit%20the%20stands%20soon)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704788640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2F6hirodn4_delhi-car-pollution_625x300_05_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fa-common-road-tax-for-entire-nation-coming-4828629%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20government%20is%20seriously%20studying%20if%20it%20could%20implement%20this%20year%20a%20pathbreaking%20idea%20of%20a%20common%20road%20tax%20for%20the%20whole%20nation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fa-common-road-tax-for-entire-nation-coming-4828629%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fa-common-road-tax-for-entire-nation-coming-4828629%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fa-common-road-tax-for-entire-nation-coming-4828629%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CEO%20kills%20son%20in%20Goa%3A%20Who%20is%20Bengaluru's%20killer%20mom%20Suchana%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704788464000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106662790%2Cimgsize-21966.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fgoa%2Fwho-is-suchana-seth-mindful-ai-lab-ceo-woman-ceo-kills-son-in-goa-what-police-said-about-bengaluru