2%3A%22%3Cp%3EGhaziabad%20near%20Delhi%20is%20likely%20to%20soon%20join%20the%20list%20of%20places%20renamed%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20amid%20demands%20by%20Hindu%20outfits.%20The%20options%20are%3A%20Gajnagar%20and%20Harnandi%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20was%20tabled%20by%20a%20BJP%20councillor%20yesterday%20and%20the%20Ghaziabad%20civic%20body%20put%20it%20on%20its%20Tuesday's%20board%20meeting%20agenda%2C%20reported%20The%20Times%20of%20India.%20With%20the%20BJP%20enjoying%20a%20comfortable%20majority%20in%20the%20civic%20body%2C%20there%20seems%20hardly%20any%20obstacle%20for%20the%20name%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20requests%20for%20renaming%20the%20city%20for%20some%20time%20and%20but%20this%20will%20be%20the%20first%20time%20it%20will%20be%20discussed%20at%20the%20executive%20level%2C%20the%20report%20quoted%20mayor%20Sunita%20Dayal%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Singh%2C%20who%20tabled%20the%20proposal%2C%20said%20Ghaziabad%20-%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20-%20holds%20a%20significant%20place%20in%20history%20and%20should%20be%20accorded%20its%20rightful%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahant%20Narayan%20Giri%2C%20the%20head%20priest%20of%20Dudheshwar%20Nath%20temple%20who%20has%20been%20leading%20the%20name-change%20efforts%2C%20said%20Ghaziabad%20was%20once%20part%20of%20Hastinapur%2C%20described%20as%20the%20capital%20of%20Kuru%20Kingdom%20in%20Hindu%20texts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20has%20led%20the%20country%20in%20renaming%20places%2C%20the%20most%20significant%20being%20that%20of%20Allahabad%2C%20which%20is%20known%20as%20Prayagraj%20since%202018.%20A%20series%20of%20name%20changes%20followed%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20had%20even%20proposed%20changing%20Ghagra%20river's%20name%20to%20Saryu%2C%20which%20finds%20mention%20in%20ancient%20Hindu%20scriptures%20and%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20flown%20through%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Faizabad%20junction%20was%20renamed%20Ayodhya%20Cantonment%20by%20the%20Railways.%20Same%20year%2C%20the%20Jhansi%20railway%20station%20was%20renamed%20Veerangana%20Laxmibai%20Railway%20Station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20gave%20its%20consent%20to%20change%20the%20names%20of%20two%20places%3A%20Mundera%20Baazar%20in%20Gorakhpur%20district%20to%20Chauri-Chaura%20and%20Telia%20Afghan%20village%20in%20Deoria%20district%20to%20Telia%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704782700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F057ibs3o_ghaziabad-station_625x300_09_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fghaziabad-news%2Fghaziabad-to-be-renamed-civic-body-to-discuss-proposal-today-4828030%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ghaziabad%20near%20Delhi%20is%20likely%20to%20soon%20join%20the%20list%20of%20places%20renamed%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20amid%20demands%20by%20Hindu%20outfits.%20The%20options%20are%3A%20Gajnagar%20and%20Harnandi%20Nagar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fghaziabad-news%2Fghaziabad-to-be-renamed-civic-body-to-discuss-proposal-today-4828030%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fghaziabad-news%2Fghaziabad-to-be-renamed-civic-body-to-discuss-proposal-today-4828030%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fghaziabad-news%2Fghaziabad-to-be-renamed-civic-body-to-discuss-proposal-today-4828030%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20top%20city%20official%20used%20a%20downtown%20billboard%20to%20secretly%20funnel%20'huge%20sums'%20of%20cash%20into%20his%20family's%20pockets%2C%20Chinese%20state%20media%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224496%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20photo%20taken%20on%20December%2018%2C%202019%20shows%20people%20walking%20past%20a%20statue%20of