d%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F2803301701%2FNACKGj5ET%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030103_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%2C%20four-part%20documentary%20series%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20state%20broadcaster%20CCTV%20about%20China's%20crackdown%20on%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20party%20secretary%2C%20Zhang%20held%20the%20top%20position%20in%20Jilin%20starting%20in%202011%20before%20being%20assigned%20vice-chairman%20of%20the%20province's%20political%20advisory%20body%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhang%2C%2066%2C%20had%20a%20son%20who%20owned%20the%20billboard%2C%20which%20was%20fitted%20onto%20a%20pedestrian%20overpass%20in%20the%20city's%20commercial%20district%2C%20per%20CCTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20owners%20seeking%20favors%20from%20Zhang%20would%20dump%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20sums%20of%20money%26quot%3B%20into%20buying%20ads%20on%20the%20billboard%2C%20even%20though%20demand%20for%20advertising%20on%20the%20billboard%20was%20relatively%20low%20by%20market%20standards%2C%20according%20to%20CCTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20companies%20discovered%20that%20the%20billboard%20was%20owned%20by%20the%20company%20of%20Party%20Secretary%20Zhang's%20son%2C%20many%20flocked%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Tang%20Zhaoyang%2C%20a%20staff%20of%20the%20Central%20Commission%20for%20Discipline%20Inspection%2C%20said%20in%20the%20documentary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20companies%20didn't%20even%20have%20advertising%20needs%2C%20but%20they%20took%20the%20initiative%20to%20buy%20these%20ads%2C%20typically%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20obtain%20benefits%20from%20Party%20Secretary%20Zhang%2C%26quot%3B%20Tang%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECCTV%20dubbed%20the%20billboard%20an%20%26quot%3Boverpass%20bridge%20of%20Zhang's%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20citing%20the%20overpass%20over%20which%20the%20display%20hangs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20broadcaster%20also%20reported%20that%20Zhang%20received%20gold%20bars%2C%20property%2C%20and%20cash%20worth%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20Chinese%20yuan%20from%20a%20businessman%20who%20was%20his%20colleague%20when%20both%20men%20started%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gifts%20were%20compensation%20for%20Zhang%20as%20he%20rose%20through%20government%20ranks%20and%20assisted%20his%20friend%20with%20state%20contracts%2C%20per%20CCTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhang%20is%20featured%20in%20a%20short%20clip%20in%20the%20documentary%2C%20wearing%20a%20black%20t-shirt%20in%20a%20gloomy%20corridor%20and%20solemnly%20expressing%20remorse%20for%20his%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20biggest%20threat%20was%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Several%20other%20disgraced%20top%20politicians%20featured%20in%20the%20documentary%20appeared%20in%20similar%20clips%2C%20apologizing%20and%20condemning%20their%20past%20behaviors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Zhang%20is%20one%20of%20dozens%20of%20top%20officials%20to%20be%20expelled%2C%20the%20alleged%20details%20of%20his%20case%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20myriad%20ways%20corruption%20seeped%20into%20China's%20top%20echelons%20of%20leadership%20for%20decades%20%E2%80%94%20and%20on%20Chinese%20leader%20Xi%20Jinping's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fchina-punished-over-600000-officials-amid-xis-corruption-clampdown-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-running%20effort%20to%20uproot%20graft%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20crackdowns%20have%20swept%20multiple%20bodies%20of%20the%20Chinese%20government%2C%20with%20a%20recent%20purge%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%20that%20reached%20as%20high%20as%20the%20defense%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Xi's%20war%20against%20corruption%20has%20also%20been%20criticized%20as%20a%20way%20for%20him%20to%20selectively%20take%20down%20political%20rivals%20and%20dissent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20leader%2C%20who%20took%20the%20top%20office%20in%202013%2C%20has%20widely%20been%20thought%20to%20have%20cemented%20near-ultimate%20power%20in%20China%20after%20the%20country's%20governing%20body%20cleared%20the%20way%20for%