%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhawan.%C2%A0%20Chirag%20and%20Satwik%20were%20presented%20the%20coveted%20Major%20Dhyan%20Chand%20Khel%20Ratna%20award%20for%20a%20breakout%202023%2C%20during%20which%20they%20won%20their%20maiden%20Asian%20Games%20gold%20--%20a%20first%20for%20India%20in%20badminton%20--%2C%20while%20also%20clinching%20the%20Asian%20Championships%20title%20and%20the%20Indonesia%20Open%20Super%201000%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20awards%20ceremony%2C%20usually%20held%20on%20August%2029%20to%20commemorate%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20hockey%20legend%20Major%20Dhyan%20Chand%2C%20was%20deferred%20because%20of%20the%20Hangzhou%20Asian%20Games%20from%20September%2023%20till%20October%208%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20atmosphere%20of%20gaiety%20pervaded%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhawan%20as%2026%20athletes%20and%20para-athletes%20were%20conferred%20the%20Arjuna%20Awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChirag%20and%20Satwik%2C%20who%20became%20world%20No.1%20last%20year%2C%20would%20be%20aiming%20for%20an%20Olympic%20medal%20in%20Paris%2C%20having%20all%20but%20sealed%20qualification%20for%20the%20global%20showpiece%20later%20this%20year%20by%20virtue%20of%20being%20world%20No.2.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%20that%20is%20our%20next%20goal%20(to%20win%20an%20Olympic%20medal).%20We%20hope%20to%20do%20the%20country%20proud%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chirag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20receiving%20a%20huge%20round%20of%20applause%20was%20the%20newly-crowned%20chess%20Grandmaster%20R.%20Vaishali%2C%20the%20elder%20sister%20of%20precocious%20chess%20talent%20R.%20Praggnanandhaa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaishali%20was%20honoured%20for%20becoming%20the%20third%20woman%20from%20the%20country%20after%20Koneru%20Humpy%20and%20Dronavalli%20Harika%20to%20turn%20GM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPistol%20shooting%20sensation%2C%2019-year-old%20Esha%20Singh%2C%20was%20among%20the%20notable%20absentees%20as%20she%20is%20competing%20in%20the%20Asian%20Olympic%20Qualifiers%20in%20Jak