y%20and%20age%20of%20social%20media%2C%20diplomacy%20is%20facing%20new%20challenges.%20At%20times%2C%20the%20cacophony%20of%20social%20media%20drowns%20out%20the%20really%20important%20issues%20that%20need%20engagement%2C%20but%20sometimes%20it%20manages%20to%20bring%20to%20the%20fore%20the%20underlying%20trends%20that%20otherwise%20would%20take%20time%20to%20shape%20up.%20The%20India-Maldives%20spat%20is%20one%20such%20case%20where%20the%20simmering%20tensions%20have%20boiled%20over%20with%20some%20needless%20comments%20from%20Male%20highlighting%20how%20the%20once-close%20neighbours%20seem%20to%20be%20drifting%20away.%20The%20rhetorical%20exuberance%20of%20some%20members%20of%20the%20new%20government%20in%20the%20Maldives%20have%20exposed%20the%20substantive%20differences%20between%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Male%20as%20well%20as%20with%20the%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Lakshadweep%20last%20week%20seems%20to%20have%20triggered%20a%20social%20media%20and%20a%20diplomatic%20storm%2C%20which%20continues%20to%20reverberate%20in%20multiple%20dimensions.%20From%20social%20media%20influencers%20to%20local%20politicians%20and%20from%20Bollywood%20celebrities%20to%20the%20strategic%20community%2C%20everyone%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20view.%20The%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20visited%20Lakshadweep%20to%20inaugurate%20the%20Kochi-Lakshadweep%20Islands%20Submarine%20Optical%20Fiber%20Connection%20and%20some%20other%20projects%20but%20while%20doing%20so%20he%20also%20took%20time%20out%20for%20some%20snorkeling%20and%20leisure%20activities%20that%20took%20social%20media%20by%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20some%20in%20India%20suggested%20that%20boosting%20tourism%20in%20Lakshadweep%20would%20be%20a%20good%20idea%2C%20some%20in%20the%20Maldives%20saw%20Modi's%20visit%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20project%20Lakshadweep%20as%20an%20alternative%20tourist%20destination%20to%20the%20Maldives.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20derogatory%20remarks%20against%20Indians%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20were%20made%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20strong%20reaction%20in%20India.%20Some%20of%20these%20comments%20came%20from%20deputy%20ministers%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Youth%20Empowerment%2C%20Information%20and%20Art%20of%20the%20Maldives%20in%20response%20to%20which%20the%20hashtag%20%23BoycottMaldives%20started%20trending%20on%20X%2C%20with%20many%20Indians%20expressing%20their%20displeasure%20and%20some%20even%20cancelling%20their%20plans%20to%20visit%20the%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20governments%20sprung%20to%20action%20quickly%2C%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20summoning%20Maldivian%20ambassador%20Ibrahim%20Shaheeb.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20Maldivian%20government%20summoning%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%2C%20Munu%20Mahawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20of%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20understood%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20has%20responded%20by%20suspending%20three%20deputy%20ministers%20for%20their%20offensive%20social%20media%20posts.%20In%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Maldivian%20ministry%20of%20foreign%20affairs%20acknowledged%20%26quot%3Bthe%20existence%20of%20derogatory%20comments%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20directed%20at%20foreign%20leaders%20and%20dignitaries%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20underlined%20that%20%26quot%3Bthese%20comments%20are%20personal%20views%20and%20do%20not%20align%20with%20the%20official%20stance%20of%20the%20Maldives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20high%20under%20Ibrahim%20Solih%2C%20relations%20between%20the%20Maldives%20and%20India%20have%20been%20on%20shaky%20grounds%20since%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20came%20to%20power.%20He%20had%20run%20his%20campaign%20on%20an%20anti-India%20platform%20%C2%A0his%20'India%20out'%20campaign%20garnered%20significant%20attention%20last%20year.%20Accusing%20India%20and%20the%20previous%20Maldivian%20government%20of%20violating%20the%20country's%20sovereignty%2C%20Muizzu%20had%20asked%20India%20to%20remove%20its%20troops%20from%20the%20country%20immediately%20after%20being%20sworn%20in.%20Turkey%20was%20Muizzu's%20first%20destination%20for%20a%20bilateral%20visit%20and%20he%20is%20in%20China%20this%20week%2C%20breaking%20a%20long%20held%20tradition%20whereby%20his%20predecessors%20used%20to%20visit%20India%20first%20after%20taking%20office.%20Male%20was%20absent%20from%20the%20Colombo%20Security%20Conclave%20meeting%20in%20December.%20And%20more%20recently%2C%20Muizzu's%20government%20decided%20to%20not%20renew%20an%20agreement%20with%20New%20Delhi%20that%20allowed%20India%20to%20conduct%20hydrographic%20surveys%20in%20Maldivian%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20crisis%20has%20further%20reinforced%20this%20divergence%20between%20two%20traditionally%20close%20neighbours.%20All%20states%20in%20South%20Asia%20and%20Indian%20Ocean%20region%20have%20to%20balance%20between%20their%20two%20regional%20behemoths%20-%20India%20and%20China.%20It%20requires%20a%20fine%20diplomatic%20balance.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20the%20Maldives%20under%20Muizzu%2C%20that%20balance%20has%20gone%20haywire%20and%20it%20is%20this%20imbalance%20that%20is%20leading%20to%20a%20dangerous%20situation%20where%20not%20only%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20governments%20but%20also%20between%20the%20two%20peoples%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20impacted%20by%20long%20term%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20domestic%20posturing%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20realisation%20in%20the%20Maldives%20in%20the%20past%20that%20India%20remains%20a%20valuable%20security%20partner%20in%20the%20region%2C%20making%20up%20for%20Male's%20scarce%20maritime%20surveillance%20capacity%20and%20capabilities.%20It%20is%20no%20coincidence%20that%20even%20Abdullah%20Yameen%2C%20under%20whose%20Presidency%20Male%20drifted%20closer%20to%20China%2C%20continued%20defence%20cooperation%20with%20India%20even%20during%20the%20roughest%20phase%20of%20bilateral%20relations.%20India%20is%20also%20the%20Maldives'%20biggest%20trade%20partner%2C%20a%20top%20export%20destination%2C%20and%20a%20traditional%20donor.%20Tourism%20sustains%20the%20economy%20of%20the%20Maldives%20and%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20visitors%20to%20the%20island%20nation%20come%20from%20India.%20It%20doesn't%20require%20great%20foresight%20to%20conclude%20that%20Male%20should%20avoid%20provoking%20New%20Delhi.%20If%20for%20New%20Delhi%20the%20Maldives%20is%20an%20important%20partner%2C%20given%20its%20critical%20geography%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20then%20for%20Male%20too%20India%20remains%20a%20critical%20economic%20and%20security%20anchor%20in%20the%20region.%20This%20makes%20it%20imperative%20that%20mutual%20sensitivities%20are%20respected%20with%20clearly%20articulated%20red-lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20His%20most%20recent%20book%20is%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20Afghan%20Muddle%26quot%3B%20(HarperCollins)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704780720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fo7415eug_maldives-generic-facebook_625x300_09_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffinding-the-right-balance-in-india-maldives-ties-4827751%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20this%20day%20and%20age%20of%20social%20media%2C%20diplomacy%20is%20facing%20new%20challenges.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffinding-the-right-balance-in-india-maldives-ties-4827751%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffinding-the-right-balance-in-india-maldives-ties-4827751%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffind