ws%2Fthe-boys-succession-astra-tv-awards-winners-1235865738%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20We%20Can't%20Forget%20What%20the%20Modi%20Government%20Did%20to%20the%20Tablighi%20Jamaat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F21113206%2Frepatriation.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20sometimes%20necessary%20to%20remind%20ourselves%20of%20the%20past%20in%20order%20to%20understand%20the%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20years%20ago%2C%20in%202020%2C%20evangelical%20Muslim%20organisation%20Tablighi%20Jamaat%20held%20a%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%20from%20March%2010%20to%2013.%20This%20was%20scheduled%20long%20before%20the%20onset%20of%20Covid-19%20and%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20was%20itself%20dismissive%20of%20the%20threat%20of%20a%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20March%2013%2C%202020%20PTI%20report%20had%20claimed%3A%20%E2%80%9CCovid-19%20is%20not%20health%20emergency%2C%20no%20need%20to%20panic%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tablighi%20meeting%20was%20held%20before%20India%20issued%20guidelines%20on%20public%20gatherings.%20But%20as%20cases%20in%20India%20began%20to%20rise%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20March%2C%20the%20government%20determined%20it%20would%20scapegoat%20Muslims%20and%20enlisted%20the%20media%20to%20do%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20made%20much%20of%20evacuating%20the%20area%20where%20the%20congregation%20was%20being%20held.%20The%20PM%20sent%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%20to%20%E2%80%9Creason%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20organisers%2C%20who%20had%20been%20asking%20for%20safe%20evacuation%20for%20days.%20The%20virus%E2%80%99%20novelty%20and%20the%20first%20deaths%20coincided%20with%20the%20Tablighi%20Jamaat%20gathering%20and%20open%20season%20was%20declared%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20main%20reason%20for%20increased%20number%20of%20cases%20is%20that%20members%20of%20the%20Tablighi%20Jamaat%20have%20travelled%20across%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Lav%20Agarwal%2C%20health%20ministry%20joint%20secretary.%20On%20April%201%2C%20BJP%20IT%20cell%20head%20Amit%20Malviya%20tweeted%20that%20the%20Tablighi%20gathering%20was%20like%20an%20%E2%80%9CIslamic%20insurrection%E2%80%9D.%20On%20April%204%2C%20MNS%20chief%20Raj%20Thackeray%20suggested%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20members%20be%20shot.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20members%20were%20jailed%20and%20booked%20under%20the%20anti-terror%20National%20Security%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%205%2C%20Lav%20Agarwal%20said%3A%20%E2%80%98The%20doubling%20rate%20in%20India%20is%204.1%20days%2C%20had%20the%20congregation%20at%20Nizamuddin%20not%20happened%20and%20additional%20cases%20not%20come%2C%20this%20would%20have%20been%20about%207.14%20days.%E2%80%9D%20As%20later%20events%20proved%2C%20this%20was%20nonsense%2C%20but%20it%20was%20par%20for%20the%20course%20for%20this%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2018%2C%20Agarwal%20made%20another%20claim%2C%20that%20the%20group%20was%20the%20dominant%20single%20cause%20of%20the%20pandemic.%20Thus%2C%20the%20poisonous%20lie%20was%20spread%20and%20its%20effect%20began%20to%20take%20place%20in%20the%20citizenry%20as%20fast%20as%20the%20COVID-19%20itself.%20A%20Hindi%20daily%20reported%20that%20Tablighi%20Jamaat%20members%20quarantined%20in%20a%20facility%20in%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Saharanpur%20had%20%E2%80%9Cdemanded%E2%80%9D%20non-vegetarian%20food%20and%20were%20defecating%20in%20the%20open%20inside%20the%20hospital.%20The%20Saharanpur%20police%20tweeted%20no%20such%20thing%20had%20happened%20and%20the%20story%20was%20taken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ftablighi-jamaat-communal-reporting-ib-ministry-coronavirus%5C%22%3ECOVID%2C%20Communal%20Reporting%20and%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20Attempt%20to%20Use%20Independent%20Media%20as%20Alibi%20for%20Inaction%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20months%20of%20active%20persecution%2C%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20members%2C%20including%20foreigners%2C%20were%20jailed%2C%20charged%20with%20attempted%20murder%20and%20provisions%20of%20Section%20269%20(%E2%80%9Cwhoever%20wilfully%20or%20negligently%20does%20any%20act%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20spread%20the%20infection%20of%20any%20disease%20dangerous%20to%20life%E2%80%9D)%20were%20invoked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20theories%20being%20promoted%20were%20that%20they%20were%20deliberately%20spreading%20the%20virus%20around%20India%20by%20getting%20themselves%20infected%2C%20spitting%20on%20fruit%2C%20refusing%20to%20wear%20masks%2C%20running%20around%20naked%20in%20their%20wards%2C%20harassing%20nurses%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20this%20was%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20noticed%20India%E2%80%99s%20malice%20against%20Muslims%20and%20it%20was%20reported%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20already%20dangerous%20to%20be%20Muslim%20in%20India.%20Then%20came%20the%20coronavirus%E2%80%9D%20(%3Cem%3ETIME%3C%2Fem%3E)%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCoronavirus%3A%20Islamophobia%20concerns%20after%20India%20mosque%20outbreak%E2%80%9D%20(%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E)%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20coronavirus%20fans%20religious%20hatred%E2%80%9D%20(%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20being%20convicted%20and%20even%20without%20any%20evidence%2C%20Jamaat%20members%20were%20%E2%80%9Cblacklisted%E2%80%9D%20from%20receiving%20visas%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ftablighi-jamaat-covid-19-communalism%5C%22%3EThe%20Tablighi%20Jamaat%20Case%20and%20How%20India%20Topped%20a%20Global%20Index%20of%20Religious%20Bias%20During%20COVID%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20amended%20the%20policy%20for%20visa%20applications%20to%20India%20to%20introduce%20a%20Tabligh-specific%20clause%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRestriction%20on%20engaging%20in%20Tabligh%20activities%20%E2%80%94%20foreign%20nationals%20granted%20any%20type%20of%20visa%20and%20OCI%20cardholders%20shall%20not%20be%20permitted%20to%20engage%20themselves%20in%20Tabligh%20work.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20restriction%20in%20visiting%20religious%20places%20and%20attending%20normal%20religious%20activities%20like%20attending%20religious%20discourses.%20However%2C%20preaching%20religious%20ideologies%2C%20making%20speeches%20in%20religious%20places%2C%20distribution%20of%20audio%20or%20visual%20display%2Fpamphlets%20pertaining%20to%20religious%20ideologies%2C%20spreading%20conversion%2C%20etc%20will%20not%20be%20allowed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20first%20time%20in%20India%20that%20a%20particular%20religious%20group%20had%20been%20mentioned%20in%20the%20list%20of%20visa%20guidelines.%20This%20was%20purely%20to%20fuel%20the%20fire%20that%20was%20already%20raging%20in%20the%20media%2C%20blaming%20the%20group%20for%20the%20deliberate%20spread%20of%20COVID-19%20in%20India%20and%20absolving%20the%20government%20from%20its%20responsibility%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20fallout%20of%20the%20disastrous%20and%20unplanned%202020%20lockdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20after%20it%20became%20generally%20accepted%20that%20the%20virus%20was%20an%20unstoppable%20global%20phenomenon%20which%20had%20spread%20through%20multiple%20ways%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CTablighi%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20story%20faded.%20On%20May%2019%2C%20the%20foreign%20members%20of%20the%20Jamaat%20moved%20court%20to%20be%20released%20from%20institutional%20quarantine%2C%20where%20they%20had%20been%20held%20for%20over%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%2C%20despite%20repeatedly%20testing%20negative%20for%20COVID-19.%20The%20government%20told%20the%20court%20that%20none%20of%20the%20visitors%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Cdetained%E2%80%9D%2C%20they%20were%20merely%20%E2%80%9Casked%20to%20join%20the%20investigation%E2%80%9D.%20But%20the%20passports%20of%20over%20700%20Jamaat%20members%20had%20been%20seized%2C%20and%20they%20were%20not%20in%20fact%2C%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftamil-nadu-detention-camp-tablighi-jamaat%5C%22%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Has%20Created%20a%20Detention%20Camp%20Just%20to%20Hold%20129%20Foreign%20Tablighi%20Jamaat%20Members%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%206%2C%20before%20the%20chief%20metropolitan%20magistrate%20at%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Saket%20court%2C%2044%20Tablighi%20Jamaat%20members%20refused%20to%20pay%20fines%20of%20between%20Rs%204%2C000%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20in%20exchange%20for%20closing%20of%20cases%20and%20bravely%20chose%20to%20face%20trial.%20By%20December%2C%20eight%20months%20after%2011%20states%20had%20filed%2020%20FIRs%20against%20more%20than%202%2C500%20Tablighi%20Jamaat%20members%2C%20nobody%20was%20convicted.%20And%20the%20courts%20fiercely%20criticised%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudges%20called%20the%20cases%20%E2%80%9Cmalicious%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20virtual%20persecution%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cabuse%20of%20process%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cabuse%20of%20power%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20said%20the%20Tablighi%20Jamaat%20members%20were%20%E2%80%9Cscapegoats%20of%20a%20political%20government%E2%80%9D%20who%20had%20acted%20against%20the%20group%20though%20having%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20an%20iota%20of%20evidence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20such%20a%20vicious%20falsehood%20was%20allowed%20to%20be%20spread%20deliberately%20should%20tell%20us%20much%20of%20what%20we%20need%20to%20understand%20about%20where%20we%20are%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Faakar-patel%5C%22%3EAakar%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704772716000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F21113206%2Frepatriation.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ftablighi-jamaat-modi-lav-agarwal-covid-19%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22That%20such%20a%20vicious%20falsehood%20was%20allowed%20to%20be%20spread%20deliberately%20should%20tell%20us%20much%20of%20what%20we%20need%20to%20understand%20about%20where%20we%20are%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ftablighi-jamaat-modi-lav-agarwal-covid-19%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20US%20Navy%20sailor%20handed%20over%20military%20secrets%20to%20China%20for%20just%20%2415%2C000%2C%20prosecutors%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Navy%20ships%20sail%20with%20vessels%20of%20the%20South%20Korean%20navy%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%20Zhao%20was%20accused%20of%20sending%20plans%20for%20a%20large%20military%20exercise%20in%20the%20region%20to%20Chinese%20intelligence.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659cbb5d6979d73718218398%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221726%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Navy%20ships%20sail%20with%20vessels%20of%20the%20South%20Korean%20navy%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%20Zhao%20was%20accused%20of%20sending%20plans%20for%20a%20large%20military%20exercise%20in%20the%20region%20to%20Chinese%20intelligence.%3Cp%3ESean%20M.%20Castellano%20US%20Navy%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20US%20Navy%20petty%20officer%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%20more%20than%202%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20spying%20for%20China.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWenheng%20Zhao%2C%2026%2C%20snagged%20%2415%2C000%20in%20exchange%20for%20plans%20on%20a%20military%20exercise%20and%20