pense%20of%20the%20backward%20and%20Dalit%20youth%2C%20who%20struggle%20for%20education%2C%20jobs%20and%20political%20space%20in%20the%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20words%20are%20common%20to%20all%20interactions%20and%20meetings%20Kishor%20has%20with%20the%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20accepts%20that%20Lalu%20gave%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvoice%20to%20the%20voiceless%E2%80%9D%20during%20his%20time%20and%20that%20Nitish%20did%20%E2%80%9Csome%20work%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20infrastructure%20sector.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20Bihar%20continues%20to%20be%20as%20backward%20as%20it%20was%20in%202005%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kishor%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20only%20%E2%80%9Cold%20and%20infirm%20people%E2%80%9D%20lived%20in%20its%20villages%20while%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20and%20more%20youths%20%5Bwere%5D%20migrating%20to%20other%20states%20to%20do%20menial%20jobs%20for%20a%20living%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fprashant-kishor-is-raring-to-go-but-does-bihars-politics-have-space-for-him%5C%22%3EPrashant%20Kishor%20Is%20Raring%20to%20Go%2C%20But%20Does%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Politics%20Have%20Space%20for%20Him%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20adds%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ceducation%20system%20has%20collapsed%20in%20the%20villages%2C%20which%20have%20become%20a%20graveyard%20of%20malnourishment%20and%20poverty%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESkilled%20in%20churning%20and%20interpreting%20data%2C%20Kishor%20tries%20to%20corroborate%20his%20statements%20with%20statistics%20related%20to%20the%20gross%20domestic%20product%20(GDP)%2C%20unemployment%2C%20malnutrition%2C%20poverty%20and%20the%20proportion%20of%20poor%20classes%20and%20marginalised%20castes%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20contends%20the%20extremely%20backward%20classes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnine-reasons-why-the-bihar-caste-census-could-shake-up-national-politics%5C%22%3Ewho%20constitute%20the%20largest%20share%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20population%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%2036.01%25%2C%20have%20no%20say%20in%20its%20economic%20space.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKishor%20embarked%20on%20his%20padyatra%20in%20Bihar%20following%20the%20failure%20of%20his%20talks%20with%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20top%20leadership%20regarding%20rebuilding%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20in%20the%20state%20and%20strengthening%20it%20against%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20he%20sounds%20more%20scathing%20towards%20Bihar%20leaders%20who%2C%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20INDIA%20coalition%20that%20has%20the%20Congress%20as%20its%20largest%20component%2C%20are%20battling%20hard%20to%20replace%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20dispensation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20picks%20holes%20in%20the%20developmental%20and%20welfare%20schemes%20of%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20but%20is%20mild%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2FHindutva%5C%22%3EHindutva%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20according%20to%20the%20opposition%20and%20a%20large%20section%20of%20public%20intellectuals%20has%20endangered%20the%20very%20basis%20of%20Indian%20democracy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPotential%20for%20damage%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPatna-based%20senior%20journalist%20Kanhaiya%20Bhelari%2C%20who%20interviewed%20Kishor%20during%20his%20padyatra%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20created%20a%20buzz%20in%20society.%20People%20are%20discussing%20him.%20He%20attracts%20a%20reasonably%20good%20crowd.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKishor%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejan%20suraaj%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20campaign%2C%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20registered%20as%20a%20political%20party%2C%20has%20a%20good%20presence%20on%20social%20media%20too%2C%20with%20his%20public%20relations%20organs%20continuously%20feeding%20his%20messages%2C%20responses%20and%20schedules%20on%20Facebook%2C%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20and%20Instagram.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20he%20has%20technically%20disassociated%20himself%20from%20I-PAC%20(the%20political%20strategy%20organisation%20he%20founded)%2C%20watchers%20of%20his%20campaign%20say%20that%20I-PAC%20workers%20were%20actively%20engaged%20in%20his%20activities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-emerges-as-a-template-to-counter-hindutva-narrative%5C%22%3EBihar%20Emerges%20as%20a%20Template%20to%20Counter%20Hindutva%20Narrative%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20although%20Kishor%20has%20not%20yet%20formed%20his%20own%20political%20party%20and%20given%20no%20indication%20that%20he%20will%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20political%20observers%20feel%20that%20his%20activities%20%E2%80%93%20if%20at%20all%20they%20gain%20momentum%20%E2%80%93%20will%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20damage%20the%20opposition%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20otherwise%20stands%20on%20a%20sticky%20wicket%20in%20Bihar%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Mahagathbandhan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsolated%20in%20Bihar%20after%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20exit%20from%20his%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20August%202022%2C%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20might%20be%20looking%20to%20Kishor%20as%20an%20%E2%80%98invisible%E2%80%99%20ally%20to%20help%20it%20in%20the%20state%2C%20where%20it%20fears%20defeat.%20As%20opposed%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20JD(U)%E2%80%99s%20cadres%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20not%20critical%20of%20Kishor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20all%2C%20he%20is%20on%20a%20good%20mission%3B%20he%20is%20doing%20good%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20said%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20might%20be%20pleasing%20to%20the%20BJP%20is%20Kishor%E2%80%99s%20repeated%20elaboration%20that%20the%20opposition%20parties%20have%20failed%20to%20develop%20a%20counter-narrative%20against%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20well-oiled%20strategy%20that%20is%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9Cnationalism%2C%20welfare%20schemes%20and%20a%20gigantic%20network%20of%20cadres%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2Fmanipur-violence%2F%5C%22%3Eprotracted%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20excesses%20on%20the%20champion%20women%20wrestlers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmp-suspensions-accountability-parliament-attack%5C%22%3Ethe%20mass%20suspension%20of%20MPs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20atrocities%20on%20minorities%2C%20the%20misuse%20of%20Union%20investigating%20agencies%20and%20the%20whimsical%20enactment%20of%20laws%20hardly%20figure%20in%20Kishor%E2%80%99s%20discourses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInitially%2C%20Nitish%20angrily%20reacted%20to%20Kishor%E2%80%99s%20statements%20alleging%20poor%20governance%20in%20Bihar%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eusko%20kuch%20pata%20hai%2C%20aap%20log%20jante%20hain%20Bihar%20mein%20kitna%20kaam%20hua%20hain%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20(%E2%80%98Does%20he%20know%20anything%2C%20you%20%5Bthe%20media%5D%20know%20how%20much%20work%20has%20been%20done%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETejashwi%20focuses%20more%20on%20the%20issues%20of%20employment%2C%20price-rise%2C%20education%20and%20communalism%20and%20ignores%20Kishor%2C%20but%20his%20cadres%20describe%20him%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstooge%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKishor%E2%80%99s%20prospects%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20interviews%20to%20the%20media%2C%20Kishor%20says%20he%20no%20longer%20likes%20to%20be%20described%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98political%20strategist%E2%80%99%20and%20prefers%20to%20be%20called%20an%20%E2%80%98activist%E2%80%99%20instead.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20while%20predicting%20%E2%80%98doom%E2%80%99%20for%20Nitish%2C%20Kishor%20repeatedly%20reminds%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20should%20remember%20how%20I%20predicted%20that%20the%20BJP%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPrashantKishor%2Fstatus%2F1340882902628749317%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewouldn%E2%80%99t%20cross%20a%20double-digit%20figure%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20against%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20West%20Bengal%20assembly%20elections.%20If%20I%20say%20that%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20party%20would%20be%20reduced%20to%20the%20single%20digits%2C%20you%20should%20trust%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20says%20to%20the%20people%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20might%20not%20have%20many%20other%20skills.%20But%20given%20my%20track%20record%2C%20you%20should%20know%20that%20I%20have%20the%20skill%20to%20get%20people%20to%20succeed%20in%20fighting%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStarting%20off%20with%20Modi%20in%202012-13%2C%20Kishor%20has%20worked%20with%20many%20political%20leaders%20across%20the%20country.%20He%20has%20achieved%20a%20fair%20amount%20of%20success%20as%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20election%20manager.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20achieving%20success%20as%20a%20behind-the-scenes%20strategist%20and%20as%20a%20political%20leader%20of%20the%20people%20are%20two%20different%20ball%20games.%20There%20is%20no%20measuring%20scale%20other%20than%20elections%20to%20measure%20if%20Kishor%20can%20make%20a%20mark%20on%20the%20politics%20of%20Bihar%20and%20of%20India%20in%20general.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKishor%20has%20so%20far%20toured%2015%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%2038%20districts%20in%20the%2016%20months%20of%20his%20padyatra%2C%20but%20he%20still%20has%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20before%20establishing%20himself%20as%20a%20meaningful%20leader%20of%20the%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20results%20of%20the%20forthcoming%20election%20might%20give%20a%20hint%20about%20his%20fate%20and%20his%20prospects%20for%20transforming%20himself%20from%20an%20election%20manager%20to%20a%20political%20leader.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fnalin-verma%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENalin%20Verma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704769258000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08235742%2FPrashant-Kishor.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fprashant-kishor-jan-suraaj-campaign-damage-opposition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20%E2%80%98jan%20suraaj%E2%80%99%20campaign%2C%20Kishor%20has%20launched%20a%20trenchant%20attack%20on%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20leaders.%20But%20achieving%20success%20as%20a%20behind-the-scenes%20strategist%20and%20as%20a%20political%20leader%20of%20the%20people%20are%20two%20different%20ball%20games.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fprashant-kishor-jan-suraaj-campaign-damage-opposition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20US%2C%20West%20Remain%20Silent%2C%20PM%20Modi%20Congratulates%20Bangladesh's%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20on%20Poll%20Win%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09084542%2FUntitled-de