d%20her%20on%20her%20victory%20for%20a%20historic%20fourth%20consecutive%20term%20in%20the%20Parliamentary%20elections.%20I%20also%20congratulate%20the%20people%20of%20Bangladesh%20for%20the%20successful%20conduct%20of%20elections.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20further%20strengthen%20our%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1744345214721126487%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20congratulated%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpeople%20of%20Bangladesh%20for%20the%20successful%20conduct%20of%20elections%E2%80%9D%20and%20added%20India%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccommitted%20to%20further%20strengthen%20our%20enduring%20and%20people-centric%20partnership%20with%20Bangladesh%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20also%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Hasina.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Monday%20morning%2C%20the%20Indian%20high%20commissioner%20to%20Dhaka%2C%20Pranay%20Verma%2C%20was%20the%20first%20foreign%20ambassador%20to%20call%20on%20Hasina.%20He%20was%20followed%20by%20envoys%20from%20China%2C%20Russia%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBhutan%2C%20Philippines%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20conspicuous%20absence%20of%20any%20congratulations%20from%20the%20United%20States%20and%20other%20western%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20Canadian%20high%20commission%20tweeted%20that%20it%20had%20not%20sent%20any%20election%20observer%20to%20Bangladesh.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20individual%20who%20identifies%20as%20a%20Canadian%20observer%20is%20acting%20independently.%20Their%20views%20have%20not%20been%20endorsed%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20Canada%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20posted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%