Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FhSEWFfYk7R%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FhSEWFfYk7R%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Bundeskanzler%20Olaf%20Scholz%20(%40Bundeskanzler)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBundeskanzler%2Fstatus%2F1744408494793437597%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20English%20Premier%20League%20said%20Beckenbauer%20will%20be%20forever%20remembered%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98Der%20Kaiser%E2%80%99%20was%20as%20elegant%20as%20he%20was%20dominant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20storied%20career%20on%20and%20off%20the%20field%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeckenbauer%20was%20one%20of%20just%20three%20people%20ever%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%20both%20as%20a%20player%20and%20a%20coach%2C%20alongside%20the%20late%20Mario%20Zagallo%20of%20Brazil%20and%20France%E2%80%99s%20Didier%20Deschamps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20his%20success%20with%20the%20national%20team%2C%20he%20earned%20numerous%20honours%20during%20his%20tenure%20at%20Bayern%20Munich%2C%20including%20three%20consecutive%20European%20Cups%20and%20the%20Intercontinental%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20coaching%2C%20Beckenbauer%20moved%20into%20football%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20made%20headlines%20in%202016%20when%20was%20fined%20by%20FIFA%E2%80%99s%20ethics%20committee%20for%20failing%20to%20co-operate%20with%20an%20inquiry%20into%20corruption%20over%20the%20awarding%20of%20the%202018%20and%202022%20World%20Cups%20in%20Russia%20and%20Qatar%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ffranz-beckenbauer-called-a-true-legend-in-global-tributes%2Fa-67921493%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704768502000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F20