20as%20a%20crucial%20gambit%20(of%20appointing%20a%20candidate%20as%20minister%20before%20his%20election)%20failed%20as%20T.T.%20lost%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echunaavi%20dangal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20(%E2%80%98electoral%20battlefield%E2%80%99).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fjaipur-news%2Frajasthan-bjp-minister-surendra-pal-loses-karanpur-bypoll-for-over-11-000-votes-101704714182801.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20T.T.%20had%20taken%20oath%20as%20a%20minister%20of%20state%20(independent%20charge)%20in%20the%20cabinet%20of%20the%20new%20chief%20minister%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma-led%20BJP%20government%20on%20December%2030%2C%20%E2%80%9Csparking%20a%20controversy%20as%20the%20Congress%20termed%20his%20oath%20as%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20election%20in%20this%20particular%20seat%20was%20delayed%20and%20held%20on%20January%205%20due%20to%20the%20death%20of%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20and%20then-MLA%2C%20Gurmeet%20Singh%20Kooner%2C%20in%20November%2C%20ten%20days%20before%20polling%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20fielded%20Kooner%E2%80%99s%20son%20Rupinder%20from%20the%20seat%20and%20the%20BJP%20put%20up%20T.T.%2C%20who%20has%20represented%20this%20seat%20two%20times%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20freshly-chosen%20MLA%20Rupinder%20Singh%20Kooner%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20my%20election%20but%20my%20father%E2%80%99s.%20I%20am%20thankful%20to%20the%20people%20that%20they%20kept%20their%20faith%20in%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%2040%20years%20of%20service%20despite%20all%20the%20political%20pressure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20T.T.%E2%80%99s%20controversial%20oath-taking%20as%20a%20minister%20while%20still%20being%20a%20candidate%20for%20the%20seat%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20a%20democratic%20country%20and%20they%20replied%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Their%20masterstroke%20has%20failed%20drastically.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CKaranpur%E2%80%99s%20people%20have%20defeated%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20arrogance.%20Their%20party%20turned%20the%20by-poll%20into%20a%20joke%20where%20the%20candidate%20could%20be%20appointed%20as%20a%20minister%20without%20being%20elected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ET.T.%20held%20the%20portfolios%20of%20the%20minority%20and%20waqf%20department%2C%20the%20agricultural%20marketing%20department%20and%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20%3Cem%3ENahar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Canal)%20department.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20T.T.%20had%20also%20served%20as%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Vasundhara%20Raje-led%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResponding%20to%20his%20defeat%20in%20the%20Karanpur%20by-poll%2C%20BJP%20state%20president%20C.P.%20Joshi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20party%20will%20review%20the%20reasons%20for%20TT%E2%80%99s%20loss%20in%20the%20by-poll.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBhajanlalBjp%2Fstatus%2F1744390152024428843%5C%22%3EChief%20minister%20Sharma%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20T.T.%20had%20%E2%80%9Chappily%20accepted%20the%20mandate%20and%20resigned%20from%20his%20post%20of%20minister%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20state%20chief%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasra%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20result%20showed%20that%20a%20government%20can%20make%20someone%20a%20minister%2C%20but%20not%20an%20MLA%2C%20for%20which%20you%20need%20the%20support%20of%20the%20people.%20The%20public%20has%20rejected%20the%20unconstitutional%20move%20taken%20by%20the%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%20poll.%3C