lawyer%20Shobha%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20two-judge%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20apex%20court%20said%20on%20Monday%20(January%208)%20that%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbilkis-bano-supreme-court-gujarat-not-competent-remission%5C%22%3Edid%20not%20have%20the%20power%20to%20grant%20premature%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%2011%20convicts%20who%20gang-raped%20a%20pregnant%20Bano%20and%20her%20family%20members%2C%20and%20also%20murdered%2014%20of%20her%20relatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convicts%20had%20been%20sentenced%20to%20life%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20feels%20like%20a%20stone%20the%20size%20of%20a%20mountain%20has%20been%20lifted%20from%20my%20chest%2C%20and%20I%20can%20breathe%20again.%20This%20is%20what%20justice%20feels%20like%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bano%E2%80%99s%20letter%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20thank%20the%20honourable%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20for%20giving%20me%2C%20my%20children%20and%20women%20everywhere%2C%20this%20vindication%20and%20hope%20in%20the%20promise%20of%20equal%20justice%20for%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20thanked%20her%20husband%20for%20children%20for%20staying%20by%20her%20side%20and%20her%20friends%20for%20%E2%80%9C%5Bholding%5D%20her%20hand%20at%20each%20difficult%20turn%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBano%20also%20thanked%20her%20lawyer%2C%20Gupta%2C%20saying%20she%20%E2%80%9Cnever%20allowed%20me%20to%20lose%20faith%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20justice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20year%20and%20half%20ago%2C%20on%20August%2015%2C%202022%2C%20when%20those%20who%20had%20destroyed%20my%20family%20and%20terrorised%20my%20very%20existence%2C%20were%20given%20an%20early%20release%2C%20I%20simply%20collapsed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20I%20had%20exhausted%20my%20reservoir%20of%20courage.%20Until%20a%20million%20solidarities%20came%20my%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20ordinary%20people%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20wrote%20appeals%20and%20open%20letters%20in%20solidarity%20with%20her%2C%20Bano%20said%2C%20saying%20they%20had%20given%20every%20woman%20in%20India%20the%20will%20to%20%E2%80%9Crescue%20the%20idea%20of%20justice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat%E2%80%99s%20government%20said%20the%20decision%20to%20remit%20the%20convicts%E2%80%99%20sentence%20was%20arrived%20at%20by%20a%20panel%20it%20had%20set%20up%2C%20comprising%20officials%20and%20%E2%80%98social%20workers%E2%80%99%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20were%20either%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20or%20were%20connected%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20division%20bench%20comprising%20Justices%20B.V.%20Nagarathna%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20said%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20%E2%80%9Cacted%20in%20complicity%20with%20the%20convicts%E2%80%9D%20and%20noted%20that%20if%20the%20convicts%20can%20%E2%80%9Ccircumvent%20the%20consequences%20of%20their%20conviction%2C%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20society%20will%20be%20reduced%20to%20a%20chimaera.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBano%20said%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20affirmed%20her%20belief%20in%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20as%20I%20absorb%20the%20full%20meaning%20of%20this%20verdict%20for%20my%20own%20life%2C%20and%20for%20my%20children%E2%80%99s%20lives%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Edua%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20emerges%20from%20my%20heart%20today%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%93%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20above%20all%20else%20and%20equality%20before%20law%2C%20for%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20full%20statement%2C%20which%20was%20also%20issued%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Hindi%2C%20is%20reproduced%20below%20in%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilkis%20Yakub%20Rasool%E2%80%99s%20Statement%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanuary%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20of%20Justice%20B.V.%20Nagarathna%20and%20Justice%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20quashed%20the%20remission%20granted%20to%20the%2011%20men%20convicted%20of%20gang-raping%20Bilkis%20Bano%20and%20murdering%2014%20members%20of%20her%20family%20in%202002%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20is%20truly%20the%20New%20Year%20for%20me.%20I%20have%20wept%20tears%20of%20relief.%20I%20have%20smiled%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20over%20a%20year%20and%20half.%20I%20have%20hugged%20my%20children.%20It%20feels%20like%20a%20stone%20the%20size%20of%20a%20mountain%20has%20been%20lifted%20from%20my%20chest%2C%20and%20I%20can%20breathe%20again.%20This%20is%20what%20justice%20feels%20like.%20I%20thank%20the%20honourable%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20for%20giving%20me%2C%20my%20children%20and%20women%20everywhere%2C%20this%20vindication%20and%20hope%20in%20the%20promise%20of%20equal%20justice%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20said%20before%2C%20and%20I%20say%20again%20today%2C%20journeys%20like%20mine%20can%20never%20be%20made%20alone.%20I%20have%20had%20my%20husband%20and%20my%20children%20by%20my%20side.%20I%20have%20had%20my%20friends%20who%20have%20given%20me%20so%20much%20love%20at%20a%20time%20of%20such%20hate%2C%20and%20held%20my%20hand%20at%20each%20difficult%20turn.%20I%20have%20had%20an%20extraordinary%20lawyer%2C%20Advocate%20Shobha%20Gupta%2C%20who%20has%20walked%20with%20me%20unwaveringly%20for%20over%2020%20long%20years%2C%20and%20who%20never%20allowed%20me%20to%20lose%20hope%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20and%20half%20ago%2C%20on%20August%2015%2C%202022%2C%20when%20those%20who%20had%20destroyed%20my%20family%20and%20terrorised%20my%20very%20existence%2C%20were%20given%20an%20early%20release%2C%20I%20simply%20collapsed.%20I%20felt%20I%20had%20exhausted%20my%20reservoir%20of%20courage.%20Until%20a%20million%20solidarities%20came%20my%20way.%20Thousands%20of%20ordinary%20people%20and%20women%20of%20India%20came%20forward.%20They%20stood%20with%20me%2C%20spoke%20for%20me%2C%20and%20filed%20PIL%20petitions%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%206000%20people%20from%20all%20over%2C%20and%208500%20people%20from%20Mumbai%20wrote%20appeals%3B%2010%2C000%20people%20wrote%20an%20Open%20Letter%2C%20as%20did%2040%2C000%20people%20from%2029%20districts%20of%20Karnataka.%20To%20each%20of%20these%20people%2C%20my%20gratitude%20for%20your%20precious%20solidarity%20and%20strength.%20You%20gave%20me%20the%20will%20to%20struggle%2C%20to%20rescue%20the%20idea%20of%20justice%20not%20just%20for%20me%2C%20but%20for%20every%20woman%20in%20India.%20I%20thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20I%20absorb%20the%20full%20meaning%20of%20this%20verdict%20for%20my%20own%20life%2C%20and%20for%20my%20children%E2%80%99s%20lives%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Edua%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20emerges%20from%20my%20heart%20today%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%93%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20above%20all%20else%20and%20equality%20before%20law%2C%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilkis%20Bano%2C%20Jan%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Issued%20through%20Adv.%20Shobha%20Gupta)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704735312000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08102157%2FUntitled-design-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftoday-i-can-breathe-again-says-bilkis-bano-after-landmark-supreme-court-judgement%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20letter%20issued%20through%20her%20lawyer%2C%20Bano%20thanked%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20her%20family%2C%20friends%20and%20lawyer%20as%20well%20as%20the%20thousands%20of%20people%20who%20extended%20their%20solidarity%20to%20her.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftoday-i-can-breathe-again-says-bilkis-bano-after-landmark-supreme-court-judgement%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boeing%20737-9%20Max%20aircraft%20to%20remain%20grounded%20until%20inspections%20compl