erindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FKathalfy-3-1704456850-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337598%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEvery%20month%2C%20Kathalfy%20caters%20to%20at%20least%20600%20orders%20from%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20without%20losing%20hope%2C%20Aman%20took%20the%20matter%20into%20his%20own%20hands.%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20try%20different%20recipes%20and%20collect%20feedback%20from%20my%20friends%20and%20neighbours.%20After%20multiple%20trials%20and%20positive%20feedback%2C%20I%20hired%20a%20professional%20chef%20to%20help%20develop%20the%20recipes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20after%20three%20years%20of%20research%20and%20development%2C%20Kathalfy%20was%20able%20to%20launch%20the%20products%20in%20April%20last%20year%2C%20though%20being%20formally%20registered%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20Indians%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20food%2C%20taste%20is%20the%20most%20important%20factor.%20Hence%20developing%20products%20that%20are%20delectable%20to%20the%20taste%20buds%20while%20retaining%20their%20nutrients%20and%20keeping%20them%20free%20of%20artificial%20chemicals%20has%20always%20been%20my%20goal.%20I%20only%20wanted%20to%20sell%20products%20that%20my%20family%20and%20I%20would%20consume%20ourselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAman%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20day%20one%2C%20I%20have%20focussed%20on%20selling%20jackfruit%20to%20uplift%20its%20social%20status.%20Unlike%20other%20brands%2C%20I%20never%20wanted%20to%20term%20it%20a%20meat%20replacement%20product.%20Instead%2C%20I%20always%20promote%20jackfruit%20for%20what%20it%20is%2C%20which%20is%20also%20reflected%20in%20our%20brand%20name%20Kathalfy%2C%20which%20is%20%3Cem%3EKathal%3C%2Fem%3E%20plus%20Simplify.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20glad%20that%20our%20customer%20base%20is%20