r%20young%20individuals.%20One%20effective%20way%20we%20showcase%20these%20products%20is%20through%20fashion-oriented%20presentations.%20For%20instance%2C%20we%20feature%20scenarios%20where%20students%2C%20fresh%20out%20of%20university%20or%20college%2C%20are%20seen%20carrying%20jute%20bags.%20This%20not%20only%20generates%20interest%20but%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20visual%20platform%20to%20display%20the%20products%20tailored%20for%20this%20age%20group%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20while%20her%20productions%20are%20going%20up%2C%20she%20still%20hopes%20that%20more%20people%20use%20jute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20her%20journey%20and%20pondering%20on%20why%20she%20chose%20inmates%20for%20this%20particular%20program%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20often%20view%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20correctional%20system%20as%20wrongdoers%20or%20offenders%2C%20carrying%20a%20mindset%20that%20they%20deserve%20punishment.%20However%2C%20when%20these%20individuals%20engage%20in%20crafting%20products%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20the%20environment%2C%20a%20shift%20in%20perception%20occurs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20begin%20to%20appreciate%20the%20positive%20contributions%2C%20and%20gradually%2C%20acceptance%20grows.%20It%20becomes%20evident%20that%2C%20given%20a%20positive%20direction%2C%20individuals%20labelled%20as%20wrongdoers%20or%20convicts%20are%20capable%20of%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFind%20her%20work%20inspiring%3F%20Buy%20her%20products%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rakshakfoundation.in%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704378304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D337520%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kolkata's%20Chaitali%20Das%20started%20her%20organisation%20Rakshak%20Foundation%20works%20with%20prison%